(343, 1, '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ —Ä–∞—Å—Ç–µ—Ç –∫–æ–ª–∏—á–µ—Å—Ç–≤–æ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ –ø–æ–ª—É—á–∞—é—Ç —Ç–∞–∫—É—é ‚Äã‚Äã–∂–µ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω—É—é –ø–ª–∞—Ç—É, –∫–∞–∫ –∏ –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–∏. –ü—Ä–∏ —ç—Ç–æ–º —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–æ–¥–∞—Ç–µ–ª–∏ –Ω–µ –∏—Å–∫–ª—é—á–∞—é—Ç, —á—Ç–æ –≤ –¥–∞–ª—å–Ω–µ–π—à–µ–º –±—É–¥—É—Ç –ø–ª–∞—Ç–∏—Ç—å –∏–º –∏ –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–û–± —ç—Ç–æ–º —Å–≤–∏–¥–µ—Ç–µ–ª—å—Å—Ç–≤—É—é—Ç —Ä–µ–∑—É–ª—å—Ç–∞—Ç—ã –∏—Å—Å–ª–µ–¥–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏—è Personnel Service –ø–æ —Ç—Ä—É–¥–æ–≤–æ–π –º–∏–≥—Ä–∞—Ü–∏–∏ –≤ –ø–µ—Ä–≤–æ–º –ø–æ–ª—É–≥–æ–¥–∏–∏ 2018 –≥–æ–¥–∞, –ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥–∞–µ—Ç –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–æ–µ –∏–∑–¥–∞–Ω–∏–µ&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.pb.pl/ukraincy-z-lepszymi-pensjami-930685\">Puls Biznesu.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–¢–∞–∫, 24% –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏—Ö —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–æ–¥–∞—Ç–µ–ª–µ–π –ø—Ä–∏–∑–Ω–∞–ª–∏, —á—Ç–æ –≥–æ—Ç–æ–≤—ã –ø–ª–∞—Ç–∏—Ç—å \"–Ω–∞ —Ä—É–∫–∏\" —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω–∏–∫–∞–º –∏–∑ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—ã –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ, —á–µ–º –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–∞–º. –í–æ –≤—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–π –ø–æ–ª–æ–≤–∏–Ω–µ –ø—Ä–æ—à–ª–æ–≥–æ –≥–æ–¥–∞ —Ç–∞–∫—É—é –≥–æ—Ç–æ–≤–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—å –≤—ã—Ä–∞–∂–∞–ª–∏ 16% –æ–ø—Ä–æ—à–µ–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö. –¢–∞–∫–æ–π —Ä–æ—Å—Ç –æ–±—ä—è—Å–Ω—è—é—Ç —Ç—Ä—É–¥–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—è–º–∏ –ø—Ä–∏ –ø–æ–∏—Å–∫–µ —Ä–∞–±–æ—á–∏—Ö –ø–æ —Å–æ–æ—Ç–≤–µ—Ç—Å—Ç–≤—É—é—â–µ–π –∫–≤–∞–ª–∏—Ñ–∏–∫–∞—Ü–∏–µ–π.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–£–∂–µ –Ω–µ–∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–µ –≤—Ä–µ–º—è –≤–æ–∑–Ω–∞–≥—Ä–∞–∂–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–æ–≤ –∏ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –ø–æ—Ö–æ–∂–∏. –ú–æ–º–µ–Ω—Ç—ã, –∫–æ–≥–¥–∞ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω–∏–∫–∞–º –∏–∑ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—ã –ø–ª–∞—Ç–∏–ª–∏ –º–µ–Ω—å—à–µ, –±—ã—Å—Ç—Ä–æ —É—à–ª–∏ –≤ –ø—Ä–æ—à–ª–æ–µ\", - —Ä–∞—Å—Å–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª –ø—Ä–µ–¥—Å–µ–¥–∞—Ç–µ–ª—å Personnel Service –ö—à–∏—à—Ç–æ—Ñ –ò–≥–ª—å–æ—Ç.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–û–Ω –æ—Ç–º–µ—Ç–∏–ª, —á—Ç–æ –ø–æ—Ç—Ä–µ–±–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—å –≤ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω–∏–∫–∞—Ö —Å –≤–æ—Å—Ç–æ–∫–∞ —Ä–∞—Å—Ç–µ—Ç, –ø–æ—ç—Ç–æ–º—É —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–æ–¥–∞—Ç–µ–ª–∏ –≥–æ—Ç–æ–≤—ã –ø—Ä–µ–¥–ª–∞–≥–∞—Ç—å –∏–º –±–æ–ª–µ–µ –ø—Ä–∏–≤–ª–µ–∫–∞—Ç–µ–ª—å–Ω—ã–µ —É—Å–ª–æ–≤–∏—è: –∂–∏–ª—å–µ, –¥–æ—Å—Ç—É–ø –∫ –∏–Ω—Ç–µ—Ä–Ω–µ—Ç—É, —Ç—Ä–∞–Ω—Å—Ñ–µ—Ä –¥–æ –º–µ—Å—Ç–∞ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç—ã, —á—Ç–æ —Ç–∞–∫–∂–µ —É–≤–µ–ª–∏—á–∏–≤–∞–µ—Ç —Ä–µ–∞–ª—å–Ω—ã–µ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∏.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ò—Å—Å–ª–µ–¥–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏–µ —Ç–∞–∫–∂–µ –ø–æ–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª–æ, —á—Ç–æ –ø–æ –º–Ω–µ–Ω–∏—é 89% –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏—Ö —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω–∏–∫–æ–≤, —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –Ω–µ –æ—Ç–±–∏—Ä–∞—é—Ç —É –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–æ–≤ —Ä–∞–±–æ—á–∏–µ –º–µ—Å—Ç–∞.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>38% –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏—Ö —Ä–∞–±–æ—á–∏—Ö —Å–∫–ª–æ–Ω—è—é—Ç—Å—è –∫ –º–Ω–µ–Ω–∏—é, —á—Ç–æ –Ω–∞–ø–ª—ã–≤ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ —Ç–æ—Ä–º–æ–∑–∏—Ç —Ä–æ—Å—Ç –∑–∞—Ä–ø–ª–∞—Ç –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ, –∞ 58% —Ä–µ—Å–ø–æ–Ω–¥–µ–Ω—Ç–æ–≤, —á—Ç–æ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –Ω–µ –∏–º–µ—é—Ç –Ω–∏–∫–∞–∫–æ–≥–æ –≤–ª–∏—è–Ω–∏—è –Ω–∞ —ç—Ç–æ—Ç –ø–æ–∫–∞–∑–∞—Ç–µ–ª—å.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–¢–∞–∫–∂–µ, —Å–æ–≥–ª–∞—Å–Ω–æ –∏—Å—Å–ª–µ–¥–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏—é, 42% –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏—Ö —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–Ω–∏–∫–æ–≤ –ø–æ–ª–æ–∂–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å–Ω–æ –Ω–∞—Å—Ç—Ä–æ–µ–Ω—ã –∫ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–∞–º, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—é—Ç –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ. –ï—â–µ 44% –Ω–∞—Å—Ç—Ä–æ–µ–Ω—ã –Ω–µ–π—Ç—Ä–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ. –¢–æ–ª—å–∫–æ 11% –æ–ø—Ä–æ—à–µ–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö –Ω–∞—Å—Ç—Ä–æ–µ–Ω—ã –Ω–µ–≥–∞—Ç–∏–≤–Ω–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–†–∞–Ω–µ–µ –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∞—è&nbsp;Gazeta Prawna&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/ukrainskie-zarobitchane-na-vtorom-meste-po-vlijaniju-na-ekonomiku-polshi-gazeta-prawna-2451209.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">–æ—Ç–º–µ—Ç–∏–ª–∞</a>, —á—Ç–æ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏–µ –∑–∞—Ä–æ–±–∏—Ç—á–∞–Ω–µ - –Ω–∞ –≤—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–º –º–µ—Å—Ç–µ –ø–æ –≤–ª–∏—è–Ω–∏—é –Ω–∞ –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫—É—é —ç–∫–æ–Ω–æ–º–∏–∫—É.&nbsp;–ü–æ –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–º –ù–∞—Ü–±–∞–Ω–∫–∞ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–∏,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/v-polshe-zajavili-chto-pochti-vse-denezhnye-perevody-sovershajut-ukrainskie-zarobitchane-2450271.html\">—É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –ø–µ—Ä–µ–≤–æ–¥—è—Ç</a>&nbsp;–±–æ–ª–µ–µ 90% –æ—Ç –≤—Å–µ–≥–æ –æ–±—ä–µ–º–∞ —Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–∑–∞–∫—Ü–∏–π –∑–∞ –≥—Ä–∞–Ω–∏—Ü—É.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–û—Ç–º–µ—Ç–∏–º, —á—Ç–æ&nbsp;–ú–∏–Ω–∏—Å—Ç–µ—Ä—Å—Ç–≤–æ —Å–æ—Ü–∏–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ–π –ø–æ–ª–∏—Ç–∏–∫–∏&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/markets/v-minsotspolitiki-sprohnozirovali-uhrozu-utechki-kadrov-iz-ukrainy-2462469.html\">–ø—Ä–æ–≥–Ω–æ–∑–∏—Ä—É–µ—Ç</a>&nbsp;–≤ –±–ª–∏–∂–∞–π—à–∏–µ –≥–æ–¥—ã —É—Å–∏–ª–µ–Ω–∏–µ –º–∏–≥—Ä–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö –ø—Ä–æ—Ü–µ—Å—Å–æ–≤ –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ –∑–∞ —Å—á–µ—Ç –≤—ã—Å–æ–∫–æ–≥–æ —Å–ø—Ä–æ—Å–∞ –Ω–∞ –∫–≤–∞–ª–∏—Ñ–∏—Ü–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω–Ω—É—é —Ä–∞–±–æ—á—É—é —Å–∏–ª—É.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '–ó–∞—Ä–ø–ª–∞—Ç–∞ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –≤ –ø–æ–ª—å—à–µ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '341-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '', 341, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/02/19/341-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(344, 1, '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Poland, the number of Ukrainians who receive the same wages as Poles is growing. At the same time, employers do not exclude that in the future they will pay them more.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is evidenced by the results of the Personnel Service study on labor migration in the first half of 2018, reports the Polish edition of <a href=\"https://www.pb.pl/ukraincy-z-lepszymi-pensjami-930685\">Puls Biznesu.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thus, 24% of Polish employers admitted that they are ready to pay &quot;on hand&quot; workers from Ukraine more than Poles. In the second half of last year, 16% of respondents expressed such readiness. This increase is explained by the difficulties in finding workers on the appropriate qualifications.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;For some time the rewards of Poles and Ukrainians are similar. The moments when workers from Ukraine were paid less were quickly a thing of the past,&quot; said Krzysztof Igligot, Chairman of Personnel Service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He noted that the need for workers from the east is growing, so employers are ready to offer them more attractive conditions: housing, access to the Internet, transfer to the place of work, which also increases real earnings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The study also showed that according to 89% of Polish workers, Ukrainians do not take away jobs from Poles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>38% of Polish workers are inclined to believe that the influx of Ukrainians hinders wage growth in Poland, and 58% of respondents that Ukrainians have no influence on this indicator.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also, according to the study, 42% of Polish workers are positive about Ukrainians who work in Poland. Another 44% are neutral. Only 11% of respondents are negative.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Earlier, Polish Gazeta Prawn<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/ukrainskie-zarobitchane-na-vtorom-meste-po-vlijaniju-na-ekonomiku-polshi-gazeta-prawna-2451209.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">a noted </a>that Ukrainian zarobitchans are the second most affected by the Polish economy.¬†According to the National Bank of <a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/v-polshe-zajavili-chto-pochti-vse-denezhnye-perevody-sovershajut-ukrainskie-zarobitchane-2450271.html\">Poland, Ukrainians tra</a>nsfer more than 90% of the total volume of transactions abroad.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It should be noted that the Ministry of Social<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/markets/v-minsotspolitiki-sprohnozirovali-uhrozu-utechki-kadrov-iz-ukrainy-2462469.html\"> Policy pred</a>icts in the coming years the strengthening of migration processes in Ukraine due to the high demand for skilled labor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Wages of Ukrainians in Poland', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '%d0%b7%d0%b0%d1%80%d0%bf%d0%bb%d0%b0%d1%82%d0%b0-%d1%83%d0%ba%d1%80%d0%b0-d0%b8%d0%bd%d1%86%d0%b5%d0%b2-d0%b2-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%bb%d1%8c%d1%88%d0%b5', '', '', '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=341', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(345, 1, '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>W Polsce ro≈õnie liczba Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w, kt√≥rzy otrzymujƒÖ takie same wynagrodzenie jak Polacy. Jednocze≈õnie pracodawcy nie wykluczajƒÖ, ≈ºe w przysz≈Ço≈õci bƒôdƒÖ p≈Çaciƒá im wiƒôcej.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dowodem na to sƒÖ wyniki badania Personnel Service na temat migracji zarobkowej w pierwszej po≈Çowie 2018 roku, donosi polskie wydanie P<a href=\"https://www.pb.pl/ukraincy-z-lepszymi-pensjami-930685\">ulsu Biznesu.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>W ten spos√≥b 24% polskich pracodawc√≥w przyzna≈Ço, ≈ºe jest gotowe zap≈Çaciƒá pracownikom &quot;na rƒôkƒô&quot; z Ukrainy wiƒôcej ni≈º Polakom. W drugiej po≈Çowie ubieg≈Çego roku 16% respondent√≥w wyrazi≈Ço takƒÖ gotowo≈õƒá. Wzrost ten t≈Çumaczy siƒô trudno≈õciami w znalezieniu pracownik√≥w na odpowiednich kwalifikacjach.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Od pewnego czasu nagrody Polak√≥w i Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w sƒÖ podobne. Momenty, w kt√≥rym pracownicy z Ukrainy op≈Çacali mniej, szybko nabra≈Çy ju≈º przesz≈Ço≈õci ‚Äì powiedzia≈Ç Krzysztof Igligot, prezes Personnel Service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zauwa≈ºy≈Ç, ≈ºe zapotrzebowanie na pracownik√≥w ze wschodu ro≈õnie, wiƒôc pracodawcy sƒÖ gotowi zaoferowaƒá im bardziej atrakcyjne warunki: mieszkanie, dostƒôp do Internetu, przeniesienie do miejsca pracy, co r√≥wnie≈º zwiƒôksza realne zarobki.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Badanie wykaza≈Ço r√≥wnie≈º, ≈ºe wed≈Çug 89% polskich pracownik√≥w Ukrai≈Ñcy nie odbierajƒÖ miejsc pracy Polakom.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>38% polskich pracownik√≥w jest sk≈Çonnych sƒÖdziƒá, ≈ºe nap≈Çyw Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w hamuje wzrost p≈Çac w Polsce, a 58% respondent√≥w, ≈ºe Ukrai≈Ñcy nie majƒÖ wp≈Çywu na ten wska≈∫nik.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ponadto, jak wynika z badania, 42% polskich pracownik√≥w pozytywnie odnosi siƒô do Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w pracujƒÖcych w Polsce. Kolejne 44% jest neutralnych. Tylko 11% respondent√≥w jest negatywnych.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wcze≈õniej &quot;Dziennik Gazeta Pols<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/ukrainskie-zarobitchane-na-vtorom-meste-po-vlijaniju-na-ekonomiku-polshi-gazeta-prawna-2451209.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ka&quot; zauwa</a>≈ºy≈Ç, ≈ºe ukrai≈Ñscy mieszka≈Ñcy sƒÖ drugim i najbardziej dotkniƒôtym przez polskƒÖ gospodarkƒô.¬†Wed≈Çug Narodowego Banku Pols<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/economics/v-polshe-zajavili-chto-pochti-vse-denezhnye-perevody-sovershajut-ukrainskie-zarobitchane-2450271.html\">kiego Ukrai≈Ñcy prze</a>noszƒÖ ponad 90% ≈ÇƒÖcznej liczby transakcji za granicƒô.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nale≈ºy zauwa≈ºyƒá, ≈ºe Ministerstwo Polityki Spo≈Çecznej<a href=\"https://nv.ua/biz/markets/v-minsotspolitiki-sprohnozirovali-uhrozu-utechki-kadrov-iz-ukrainy-2462469.html\"> przewiduje w</a> najbli≈ºszych latach wzmocnienie proces√≥w migracyjnych na Ukrainie ze wzglƒôdu na du≈ºe zapotrzebowanie na wykwalifikowanƒÖ si≈Çƒô roboczƒÖ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Zarobki Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w w Polsce', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '%d0%b7%d0%b0%d1%80%d0%bf%d0%bb%d0%b0%d1%82%d0%b0-%d1%83%d0%ba%d1%80%d0%b0%b8%d0%bd%d1%86%d0%b5%d0%b2-d0%b2-%d0%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%bb%d1%8c%d1%88%d0%b5', '', '', '2020-02-19 18:56:40', '2020-02-19 15:56:40', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=341', 0, 'post', '', 0);
