–ª—ã—Ö 38 —Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ö–æ–≤—ã—Ö –∫–æ–º–ø–∞–Ω–∏–π. –°–µ–π—á–∞—Å –ø–æ–∫–∞ –∏—Ö —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ 6 –æ—Å—Ç–∞–≤–∏–ª–∏</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –º–æ–≥—É—Ç –≤—ã–±–∏—Ä–∞—Ç—å: –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑—ã–≤–∞—Ç—å –¥–æ—Ä–æ–≥—É—é —Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ö–æ–≤–∫—É –∏ –ø–æ–∫—Ä—ã—Ç—å –≤—Å–µ –Ω–µ—Å—á–∞—Å—Ç–Ω—ã–µ —Å–ª—É—á–∞–∏ –∑–∞ –≥—Ä–∞–Ω–∏—Ü–µ–π –∏–ª–∏ –∫—É–ø–∏—Ç—å –¥–µ—à–µ–≤—É—é. –°—Ç–æ–∏–º–æ—Å—Ç—å –≤–∏–∑—ã –±—É–¥–µ—Ç –¥–µ—à–µ–≤–ª–µ –≤ —Ç–∞–∫–æ–º —Å–ª—É—á–∞–µ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–í–∏–∑–æ–≤—ã–π –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–í–∏–∑–æ–≤—ã–π –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä –æ—Å—Ç–∞–µ—Ç—Å—è –±–µ–∑ –∏–∑–º–µ–Ω–µ–Ω–∏–π</strong>. –ù–æ –º–æ–∂–Ω–æ –ø–µ—Ä–µ–∫—Ä—ã–≤–∞—Ç—å –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä –ø–æ—Å–ª–µ –ø–æ–ª—É–≥–æ–¥–æ–≤–æ–π –≤–∏–∑—ã. –≠—Ç–æ –¥–µ–ª–∞–µ—Ç—Å—è –ø—É—Ç–µ–º –æ—Ç–∫—Ä—ã—Ç–∏—è –≥–æ–¥–æ–≤–æ–π –≤–æ–µ–≤–æ–¥—Å–∫–æ–π –≤–∏–∑—ã.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–¢—Ä—É–¥–æ—É—Å—Ç—Ä–æ–π—Å—Ç–≤–æ –¥–ª—è –≥—Ä–∞–∂–¥–∞–Ω –ê–∑–∏–∏</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–ü–æ–ª—å—à–∞ –æ—Ñ–∏—Ü–∏–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ –æ—Ç–∫—Ä—ã–ª–∞ –¥–æ—Å—Ç—É–ø –∫ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–µ —É —Å–µ–±—è –Ω–∞ —Ç–µ—Ä—Ä–∏—Ç–æ—Ä–∏–∏ –≥—Ä–∞–∂–¥–∞–Ω–∞–º –°—Ä–µ–¥–Ω–µ–π –ê–∑–∏–∏</strong>. –ö–∞–∫ —ç—Ç–æ –ø–æ–≤–ª–∏—è–µ—Ç –Ω–∞ –∫–æ–Ω–∫—É—Ä–µ–Ω—Ü–∏—é –Ω–∞ —Ä—ã–Ω–∫–µ —Ç—Ä—É–¥–∞ ‚Äî –±—É–¥–µ–º —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –≥–∞–¥–∞—Ç—å. –ù–æ –æ–¥–Ω–æ –ø–æ–Ω—è—Ç–Ω–æ: –∫—Ç–æ —É—Å—Ç—Ä–∞–∏–≤–∞–ª —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –Ω–µ–ª–µ–≥–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ –Ω–∞ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç—É –∑–∞ 11-12 –∑–ª–æ—Ç—ã—Ö, –±—É–¥—É—Ç –±—Ä–∞—Ç—å –∞–∑–∏–∞—Ç–æ–≤ –Ω–∞ —Å—Ç–∞–≤–∫—É –Ω–∏–∂–µ. –û–¥–Ω–æ–∑–Ω–∞—á–Ω–æ —Ç–∞–∫ –±—É–¥–µ—Ç.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í—Å–µ –º—ã –∑–Ω–∞–µ–º, —á—Ç–æ –º–∏–Ω–∏–º—É–º 30 –ø—Ä–æ—Ü–µ–Ω—Ç–æ–≤ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—é—Ç –Ω–µ –æ—Ñ–∏—Ü–∏–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ. –ü—Ä–∏–¥–µ—Ç—Å—è –æ—Ç–∫—Ä—ã–≤–∞—Ç—å –≤–∏–∑—ã –∏ –ø—Ä–∏–¥–µ—Ä–∂–∏–≤–∞—Ç—å—Å—è –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∏–ª.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í –ª—é–±–æ–º —Å–ª—É—á–∞–µ,&nbsp;—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ —Å–æ —Å–≤–æ–∏–º–∏ –Ω–æ–≤–æ–≤–≤–µ–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è–º–∏ –∏ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–º–∏ –∑–∞–∫–æ–Ω–∞–º–∏&nbsp;–≤—Å–µ —Ä–∞–≤–Ω–æ –±—É–¥–µ—Ç –ø—Ä–∏–≤–ª–µ–∫–∞—Ç—å –º–∏–ª–ª–∏–æ–Ω—ã –∑–∞—Ä–æ–±–∏—Ç—á–∞–Ω. –û–Ω–∞ —Å—Ç–∞–Ω–µ—Ç—Å—è –ª–∏–¥–µ—Ä–æ–º —Å—Ä–µ–¥–∏ –¥—Ä—É–≥–∏—Ö –µ–≤—Ä–æ–ø–µ–π—Å–∫–∏—Ö —Å—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω –ø–æ –∫–æ–ª–∏—á–µ—Å—Ç–≤—É –∏–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö —Ç—Ä—É–¥–æ–≤—ã—Ö –º–∏–≥—Ä–∞–Ω—Ç–æ–≤.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '–ù–æ–≤–æ–µ 2020', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '', 383, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/02/25/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(387, 1, '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Raising the salaries of young people</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The innovation applies to young people under the age of 26. What does that mean?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you work officially in Poland and you are under 26 years old, the state returns taxes from your salary to your bank card AUTOMATICALLY</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Until 2020, it was necessary to make manual declarations and only after a while the money was returned.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Visa-free visa after visa</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you have worked in Poland on a visa and you have a biometric passport, you can stay for up to 90 days without leaving for Ukraine</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is important: in order to avoid problems and deportation in the worst case, we warn that it will not work officially these 90 days. If you get caught at work, you&#39;ll be in trouble.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>38 insurance companies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Consulate confirmed the fact that from the new year it is possible to use the services of as many as 38 insurance companies. So far, only six have left</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrainians can choose: order expensive insurance and cover all accidents abroad or buy cheap. The cost of the visa will be cheaper in this case.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Visa corridor</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The visa corridor remains unchanged</strong>. But you can block the corridor after a six-month visa. This is done by opening an annual governor&#39;s visa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Employment for Asian citizens</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Poland has officially opened access to work in its territory to Central Asian citizen</strong>s. How this will affect competition in the labor market - we will only guess. But one thing is clear: who arranged Ukrainians illegally to work for 11-12 zlotys, will take Asians on a bet lower. Definitely so.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We all know that at least 30 percent of Ukrainians do not work officially. We&#39;ll have to open visas and follow the rules.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In any case, working in Poland with its own innovations and new laws will still attract millions of people. It will become a leader among other European countries in the number of foreign migrant workers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'New 2020', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%be%d0%b5-2020-2', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=383', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(388, 1, '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Podnoszenie wynagrodze≈Ñ m≈Çodych ludzi</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Innowacja dotyczy m≈Çodych ludzi poni≈ºej 26 roku ≈ºycia. Co to oznacza?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Je≈õli pracujesz oficjalnie w Polsce i masz mniej ni≈º 26 lat, pa≈Ñstwo automatycznie zwraca podatki z twojego wynagrodzenia na kartƒô bankowƒÖ</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do 2020 r. konieczne by≈Ço sk≈Çadanie rƒôcznych deklaracji i dopiero po pewnym czasie pieniƒÖdze zosta≈Çy zwr√≥cone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Wiza bezwizowa po wizy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Je≈õli pracowa≈Çe≈õ w Polsce na podstawie wizy i masz paszport biometryczny, mo≈ºesz zostaƒá do 90 dni bez wyjazdu na Ukrainƒô</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To wa≈ºne: aby uniknƒÖƒá problem√≥w i deportacji w najgorszym przypadku, ostrzegamy, ≈ºe nie bƒôdzie dzia≈Çaƒá oficjalnie te 90 dni. Je≈õli zostaniesz z≈Çapany w pracy, bƒôdziesz w tarapatach.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>38 firm ubezpieczeniowych</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Konsulat potwierdzi≈Ç fakt, ≈ºe od nowego roku mo≈ºliwe jest korzystanie z us≈Çug a≈º 38 firm ubezpieczeniowych. Do tej pory pozosta≈Ço tylko sze≈õ</strong>ƒá.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrai≈Ñcy mogƒÖ wybraƒá: zam√≥wiƒá drogie ubezpieczenie i pokryƒá wszystkie wypadki za granicƒÖ lub kupiƒá tanie. Koszt wizy bƒôdzie ta≈Ñszy w tym przypadku.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Korytarz wizowy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Korytarz wizowy pozostaje niezmieniony</strong>. Ale mo≈ºesz zablokowaƒá korytarz po sze≈õciomiesiƒôcznej wizy. Odbywa siƒô to poprzez otwarcie rocznej wizy gubernatora.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Zatrudnienie dla obywateli Azjatyckich</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Polska oficjalnie otworzy≈Ça dostƒôp do pracy na swoim terytorium dla obywateli Azji ≈örodkowe</strong>j. Jak wp≈Çynie to na konkurencjƒô na rynku pracy - zgadniemy tylko. Ale jedno jest jasne: kto nielegalnie zorganizowa≈Ç Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w do pracy za 11-12 z≈Çotych, we≈∫mie Azjat√≥w na zak≈Çad ni≈ºej. Zdecydowanie tak.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wszyscy wiemy, ≈ºe co najmniej 30 procent Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w nie pracuje oficjalnie. Bƒôdziemy musieli otworzyƒá wizy i przestrzegaƒá zasad.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>W ka≈ºdym razie praca w Polsce z w≈Çasnymi innowacjami i nowymi przepisami nadal przyciƒÖgnie miliony ludzi. Stanie siƒô liderem w≈õr√≥d innych kraj√≥w europejskich pod wzglƒôdem liczby zagranicznych pracownik√≥w migrujƒÖcych.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nowy 2020', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%be%d0%b5-2020-3', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=383', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(389, 1, '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–ü—ñ–¥–≤–∏—â–µ–Ω–Ω—è –∑–∞—Ä–ø–ª–∞—Ç –º–æ–ª–æ–¥–∏–º –ª—é–¥—è–º</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ù–æ–≤–æ–≤–≤–µ–¥–µ–Ω–Ω—è –ø–æ—à–∏—Ä—é—î—Ç—å—Å—è –Ω–∞ –º–æ–ª–æ–¥–∏—Ö –ª—é–¥–µ–π –≤—ñ–∫–æ–º –¥–æ 26 —Ä–æ–∫—ñ–≤. –©–æ —Ü–µ –∑–Ω–∞—á–∏—Ç—å?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–Ø–∫—â–æ –≤–∏ –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é—î—Ç–µ –æ—Ñ—ñ—Ü—ñ–π–Ω–æ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—â—ñ, —ñ –≤–∏ –º–æ–ª–æ–¥—à–µ 26 —Ä–æ–∫—ñ–≤, –¥–µ—Ä–∂–∞–≤–∞ –ø–æ–≤–µ—Ä—Ç–∞—î –ø–æ–¥–∞—Ç–∫–∏ –∑ –≤–∞—à–æ—ó –∑–∞—Ä–ø–ª–∞—Ç–∏ –Ω–∞ –≤–∞—à—É –±–∞–Ω–∫—ñ–≤—Å—å–∫—É –∫–∞—Ä—Ç—É –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–∞—Ç–∏—á–Ω–æ</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–î–æ 2020, –Ω–µ–æ–±—Ö—ñ–¥–Ω–æ –±—É–ª–æ –∑—Ä–æ–±–∏—Ç–∏ –∑–∞—è–≤–∏ –≤—Ä—É—á–Ω—É —ñ —Ç—ñ–ª—å–∫–∏ —á–µ—Ä–µ–∑ –¥–µ—è–∫–∏–π —á–∞—Å –≥—Ä–æ—à—ñ –±—É–ª–∏ –ø–æ–≤–µ—Ä–Ω—É—Ç—ñ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–í—ñ–∑–∞ –±–µ–∑ –≤—ñ–∑ –ø—ñ—Å–ª—è –≤—ñ–∑–∏</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–Ø–∫—â–æ –≤–∏ –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é–≤–∞–ª–∏ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—â—ñ –Ω–∞ –≤—ñ–∑—É —ñ –º–∞—î—Ç–µ –±—ñ–æ–º–µ—Ç—Ä–∏—á–Ω–∏–π –ø–∞—Å–ø–æ—Ä—Ç, —Ç–æ –º–æ–∂–µ—Ç–µ –∑—É–ø–∏–Ω–∏—Ç–∏—Å—è –¥–æ 90 –¥–Ω—ñ–≤, –Ω–µ –≤–∏—Ö–æ–¥—è—á–∏ –∑–∞ –£–∫—Ä–∞—ó–Ω—É</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í–∞–∂–ª–∏–≤–æ: –¥–ª—è —Ç–æ–≥–æ, —â–æ–± —É–Ω–∏–∫–Ω—É—Ç–∏ –ø—Ä–æ–±–ª–µ–º —ñ –¥–µ–ø–æ—Ä—Ç–∞—Ü—ñ—ó –≤ –≥—ñ—Ä—à–æ–º—É –≤–∏–ø–∞–¥–∫—É, –º–∏ –ø–æ–ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥–∂–∞—î–º–æ, —â–æ –≤—ñ–Ω –Ω–µ –±—É–¥–µ –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é–≤–∞—Ç–∏ –æ—Ñ—ñ—Ü—ñ–π–Ω–æ —Ü—ñ 90 –¥–Ω—ñ–≤. –Ø–∫—â–æ –≤–∏ –ø–æ—Ç—Ä–∞–ø–∏–ª–∏ –Ω–∞ —Ä–æ–±–æ—Ç—É, –≤–∏ –±—É–¥–µ—Ç–µ –≤ –±—ñ–¥—ñ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>38 —Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ö–æ–≤—ñ –∫–æ–º–ø–∞–Ω—ñ—ó</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–ö–æ–Ω—Å—É–ª—å—Å—Ç–≤–æ –ø—ñ–¥—Ç–≤–µ—Ä–¥–∏–≤ —Ç–æ–π —Ñ–∞–∫—Ç, —â–æ –∑ –Ω–æ–≤–æ–≥–æ —Ä–æ–∫—É –º–æ–∂–Ω–∞ –∫–æ—Ä–∏—Å—Ç—É–≤–∞—Ç–∏—Å—è –ø–æ—Å–ª—É–≥–∞–º–∏ —Ü—ñ–ª–∏—Ö 38 —Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ö–æ–≤–∏—Ö –∫–æ–º–ø–∞–Ω—ñ–π. –ü–æ–∫–∏ —â–æ –∑–∞–ª–∏—à–∏–ª–æ—Å—è –ª–∏—à–µ —à—ñ—Å—Ç—å</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–£–∫—Ä–∞—ó–Ω—Ü—ñ –º–æ–∂—É—Ç—å –≤–∏–±—Ä–∞—Ç–∏: –∑–∞–º–æ–≤–∏—Ç–∏ –¥–æ—Ä–æ–≥–µ —Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ö—É–≤–∞–Ω–Ω—è —ñ –ø–æ–∫—Ä–∏—Ç–∏ –≤—Å—ñ –Ω–µ—â–∞—Å–Ω—ñ –≤–∏–ø–∞–¥–∫–∏ –∑–∞ –∫–æ—Ä–¥–æ–Ω–æ–º –∞–±–æ –∫—É–ø–∏—Ç–∏ –¥–µ—à–µ–≤–æ. –í–∞—Ä—Ç—ñ—Å—Ç—å –≤—ñ–∑–∏ –æ–±—ñ–π–¥–µ—Ç—å—Å—è –¥–µ—à–µ–≤—à–µ –≤ —Ü—å–æ–º—É –≤–∏–ø–∞–¥–∫—É.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–í—ñ–∑–æ–≤–∏–π –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–í—ñ–∑–æ–≤–∏–π –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä –∑–∞–ª–∏—à–∞—î—Ç—å—Å—è –Ω–µ–∑–º—ñ–Ω–Ω–∏–º</strong>. –ê–ª–µ –≤–∏ –º–æ–∂–µ—Ç–µ –∑–∞–±–ª–æ–∫—É–≤–∞—Ç–∏ –∫–æ—Ä–∏–¥–æ—Ä –ø—ñ—Å–ª—è —à–µ—Å—Ç–∏–º—ñ—Å—è—á–Ω–æ—ó –≤—ñ–∑–∏. –¶–µ —Ä–æ–±–∏—Ç—å—Å—è —à–ª—è—Ö–æ–º –≤—ñ–¥–∫—Ä–∏—Ç—Ç—è —â–æ—Ä—ñ—á–Ω–æ—ó –≤—ñ–∑–∏ –≥—É–±–µ—Ä–Ω–∞—Ç–æ—Ä–∞.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>–ü—Ä–∞—Ü–µ–≤–ª–∞—à—Ç—É–≤–∞–Ω–Ω—è –¥–ª—è –≥—Ä–æ–º–∞–¥—è–Ω –ê–∑—ñ—ó</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>–ü–æ–ª—å—â–∞ –æ—Ñ—ñ—Ü—ñ–π–Ω–æ –≤—ñ–¥–∫—Ä–∏–ª–∞ –¥–æ—Å—Ç—É–ø –¥–æ —Ä–æ–±–æ—Ç–∏ –Ω–∞ —Å–≤–æ—ó–π —Ç–µ—Ä–∏—Ç–æ—Ä—ñ—ó –¥–ª—è –¶–µ–Ω—Ç—Ä–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ–∞–∑—ñ–∞—Ç—Å—å–∫–∏—Ö –≥—Ä–æ–º–∞–¥—è</strong>–Ω. –Ø–∫ —Ü–µ –≤–ø–ª–∏–Ω–µ –Ω–∞ –∫–æ–Ω–∫—É—Ä–µ–Ω—Ü—ñ—é –Ω–∞ —Ä–∏–Ω–∫—É –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—ñ-–º–∏ —Ç—ñ–ª—å–∫–∏ –∑–¥–æ–≥–∞–¥–∞—î–º–æ—Å—è. –ê–ª–µ —è—Å–Ω–æ –æ–¥–Ω–µ: —Ö—Ç–æ –æ—Ä–≥–∞–Ω—ñ–∑—É–≤–∞–≤ —É–∫—Ä–∞—ó–Ω—Ü—è–º –Ω–µ–∑–∞–∫–æ–Ω–Ω–æ –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é–≤–∞—Ç–∏ –∑–∞ 11-12 –∑–ª–æ—Ç–∏—Ö, –≤—ñ–∑—å–º–µ –∞–∑—ñ–∞—Ç—ñ–≤ –Ω–∞ –ø–∞—Ä—ñ –Ω–∏–∂—á–µ. –¢–æ—á–Ω–æ —Ç–∞–∫.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ú–∏ –≤—Å—ñ –∑–Ω–∞—î–º–æ, —â–æ –ø—Ä–∏–Ω–∞–π–º–Ω—ñ 30 –≤—ñ–¥—Å–æ—Ç–∫—ñ–≤ —É–∫—Ä–∞—ó–Ω—Ü—ñ–≤ –Ω–µ –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é—é—Ç—å –æ—Ñ—ñ—Ü—ñ–π–Ω–æ. –ù–∞–º –¥–æ–≤–µ–¥–µ—Ç—å—Å—è –≤—ñ–¥–∫—Ä–∏–≤–∞—Ç–∏ –≤—ñ–∑–∏ —ñ –¥–æ—Ç—Ä–∏–º—É–≤–∞—Ç–∏—Å—è –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∏–ª.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–£ –±—É–¥—å-—è–∫–æ–º—É –≤–∏–ø–∞–¥–∫—É, –ø—Ä–∞—Ü—é—é—á–∏ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—â—ñ –∑ –≤–ª–∞—Å–Ω–∏–º–∏ —ñ–Ω–Ω–æ–≤–∞—Ü—ñ—è–º–∏ —ñ –Ω–æ–≤–∏–º–∏ –∑–∞–∫–æ–Ω–∞–º–∏, –≤—Å–µ –æ–¥–Ω–æ –ø—Ä–∏–≤–µ—Ä–Ω—É—Ç—å –º—ñ–ª—å–π–æ–Ω–∏ –ª—é–¥–µ–π. –í–æ–Ω–∞ —Å—Ç–∞–Ω–µ –ª—ñ–¥–µ—Ä–æ–º —Å–µ—Ä–µ–¥ —ñ–Ω—à–∏—Ö —î–≤—Ä–æ–ø–µ–π—Å—å–∫–∏—Ö –∫—Ä–∞—ó–Ω —É –∫—ñ–ª—å–∫–æ—Å—Ç—ñ —ñ–Ω–æ–∑–µ–º–Ω–∏—Ö —Ç—Ä—É–¥—è—â–∏—Ö-–º—ñ–≥—Ä–∞–Ω—Ç—ñ–≤.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '–ù–æ–≤–∏–π 2020', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'd0-bd-d0-%d0%b1%d1%83%d1%82%d0%b8-d0-b2-d0-be-d0-b5-2020', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:39:51', '2020-02-25 14:39:51', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=383', 0, 'post', '', 0);
