(401, 1, '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –æ—Å–≤–∞–∏–≤–∞—é—Ç –Ω–æ–≤—ã–π –≤–∏–¥ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∞ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ. –ï—Å–ª–∏ —Ä–∞–Ω—å—à–µ –º–∞—Å—Å–æ–≤–æ –µ—Ö–∞–ª–∏ –Ω–∞ —Å—Ç—Ä–æ–π–∫–∏, —Ç–æ —Ç–µ–ø–µ—Ä—å —É—Å—Ç—Ä–∞–∏–≤–∞—é—Ç—Å—è –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—è–º–∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ Uber –∏ Bolt, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—é—Ç —á–µ—Ä–µ–∑ –º–æ–±–∏–ª—å–Ω—ã–µ –ø—Ä–∏–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏—è.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ü—Ä–∏–±—ã–ª—å - –æ—Ç 25 –¥–æ 50 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á –≥—Ä–∏–≤–µ–Ω.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–î–ª—è —ç—Ç–æ–≥–æ –Ω—É–∂–Ω—ã —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏–µ –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞ - —Ç–∞–∫—Å–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å –º–æ–∂–Ω–æ –ø–æ \"–±–µ–∑–≤–∏–∑—É\" —Ç—Ä–∏ –º–µ—Å—è—Ü–∞ –±–µ–∑ —Ä–∞–∑—Ä–µ—à–µ–Ω–∏–π, –∑–∞—Ç–µ–º –≤–æ–∑–≤—Ä–∞—â–∞—é—Ç—Å—è –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—É –Ω–∞ —Ç—Ä–∏ –º–µ—Å—è—Ü–∞ –∏ —Å–Ω–æ–≤–∞ –µ–¥—É—Ç –Ω–∞ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∏.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–¢–∞–∫ –∫–∞–∫ –Ω–∞ —Å–≤–æ–∏—Ö –º–∞—à–∏–Ω–∞—Ö —Å —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏–º–∏ –Ω–æ–º–µ—Ä–∞–º–∏ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–∏ –Ω–µ –º–æ–≥—É—Ç —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—Ç—å, –±–µ—Ä—É—Ç –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–æ–±–∏–ª–∏ –Ω–∞–ø—Ä–æ–∫–∞—Ç –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ - –≤ —Å—Ä–µ–¥–Ω–µ–º –ø–æ 500 –∑–ª–æ—Ç—ã—Ö –≤ –Ω–µ–¥–µ–ª—é (3 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á–∏ –≥—Ä–∏–≤–µ–Ω).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ù–æ –µ—Å—Ç—å –∏ –ø–æ–¥–≤–æ–¥–Ω—ã–µ –∫–∞–º–Ω–∏ - —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏–µ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–∏ –≤—Å–µ —á–∞—â–µ –∂–∞–ª—É—é—Ç—Å—è –Ω–∞ –ø—Ä–∏—Ç–µ—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–∏—è –∏–∑-–∑–∞ –Ω–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ—Å—Ç–∏.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–°—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–∞\" —É–∑–Ω–∞–ª–∞, –∫–∞–∫ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞–µ—Ç—Å—è —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–∞–º —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç–∞–º–∏ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>–ó–∞ –ø–æ–ª–≥–æ–¥–∞ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞–ª –Ω–∞ —Å–≤–æ—é –º–∞—à–∏–Ω—É&nbsp;</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–í –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ –Ω–∞–º–Ω–æ–≥–æ –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ —à–∞–Ω—Å–æ–≤ –≤—Å—Ç—Ä–µ—Ç–∏—Ç—å –≤ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—è-—É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–∞, —á–µ–º –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–∞. –£ –Ω–µ–∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã—Ö –º–µ—Å—Ç–Ω—ã—Ö —ç—Ç–æ –≤—ã–∑—ã–≤–∞–µ—Ç —Ä–∞–∑–¥—Ä–∞–∂–µ–Ω–∏–µ. –ù–∞ –º–æ–µ–≥–æ –¥—Ä—É–≥–∞, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–π —Ç–æ–∂–µ —Ç–∞–∫—Å—É–µ—Ç –≤ –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ, –¥–≤–æ–µ –º–æ–ª–æ–¥—ã—Ö –∫–ª–∏–µ–Ω—Ç–æ–≤ –Ω–∞–µ—Ö–∞–ª–∏, –∫–æ–≥–¥–∞ –ø–æ–Ω—è–ª–∏, —á—Ç–æ –æ–Ω —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ—Ü. –ú–æ–ª, —á–µ–≥–æ —Ç—ã —Å—é–¥–∞ –ø—Ä–∏–µ—Ö–∞–ª, \"–±–∞–Ω–¥–µ—Ä–æ–≤–µ—Ü\", –∫—Ä–∏—á–∞–ª–∏, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã \"–≤–∞–ª–∏–ª –Ω–∞–∑–∞–¥ –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—É\", - —Ä–∞—Å—Å–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª –Ω–∞–º –ª—å–≤–æ–≤—è–Ω–∏–Ω –í–ª–∞–¥–∏–º–∏—Ä –ó–∞–¥–æ—Ä–æ–∂–Ω—ã–π, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–π —Ç–∞–∫—Å—É–µ—Ç –≤ –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–£—Å—Ç—Ä–æ–∏—Ç—å—Å—è –ø—Ä–æ—â–µ –≤—Å–µ–≥–æ –≤ Uber, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–π –ø–æ—Å–ª–µ–¥–Ω–∏–µ –ø—è—Ç—å –ª–µ—Ç —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞–µ—Ç –≤ –∫—Ä—É–ø–Ω–µ–π—à–∏—Ö –∏ –ø–æ–ø—É–ª—è—Ä–Ω—ã—Ö –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏—Ö –≥–æ—Ä–æ–¥–∞—Ö: –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ, –ö—Ä–∞–∫–æ–≤–µ, –ì–¥–∞–Ω—å—Å–∫–µ. –û–Ω –ø–æ–ø—É–ª—è—Ä–Ω–µ–µ –ø—Ä–æ—Å—Ç—ã—Ö —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ –∏ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–æ–∫ —Ç–∞–º –≤—ã—à–µ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ü–æ –µ–≥–æ —Å–ª–æ–≤–∞–º, –≤—ã–≥–æ–¥–Ω–µ–µ –≤—Å–µ–≥–æ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—Ç—å –≤ –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ - –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑–æ–≤ –º–Ω–æ–≥–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–ü–ª–∞—á—É –Ω–∞–ª–æ–≥ - –≤ –ø–µ—Ä–µ–≤–æ–¥–µ –Ω–∞ –Ω–∞—à–∏ –¥–µ–Ω—å–≥–∏ 7 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á –≥—Ä–∏–≤–µ–Ω –∑–∞ –º–∞—à–∏–Ω—É, –æ–∫–æ–ª–æ 5% –ø—Ä–∏–±—ã–ª–∏ –æ—Ç–¥–∞—é –∫–æ–º–ø–∞–Ω–∏–∏. –•–æ—Ä–æ—à–æ, —á—Ç–æ —Å–∞–º —Å–µ–±–µ —Ö–æ–∑—è–∏–Ω, –Ω–∞—á–∞–ª—å—Å—Ç–≤–∞ –Ω–µ—Ç, –≥—Ä–∞—Ñ–∏–∫ —Å—Ç—Ä–æ—é –ø–æ–¥ —Å–µ–±—è. –ù—É –∞ –≥–ª–∞–≤–Ω–æ–µ - –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–∞—Ç—ã–≤–∞—é –ø—Ä–∏–º–µ—Ä–Ω–æ –≤–¥–≤–æ–µ –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ, —á–µ–º –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ. –¢—É—Ç –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑–æ–≤ –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ, —É –ª—é–¥–µ–π –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ –¥–µ–Ω–µ–≥ (—Ö–æ—Ç—è —Ç–∞—Ä–∏—Ñ –ø—Ä–∏–º–µ—Ä–Ω–æ —Ç–∞–∫–æ–π –∂–µ - –æ–∫–æ–ª–æ 50 –≥—Ä–∏–≤–µ–Ω –∑–∞ 3 –∫–∏–ª–æ–º–µ—Ç—Ä–∞). –î–ª—è —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç—ã –Ω—É–∂–Ω—ã —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞, —Å–ø—Ä–∞–≤–∫–∞ –æ –Ω–µ—Å—É–¥–∏–º–æ—Å—Ç–∏ –∏ –º–∞—à–∏–Ω–∞. –í –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ —Å–Ω–∏–º–∞—é —É–≥–æ–ª –∑–∞ 200 –¥–æ–ª–ª–∞—Ä–æ–≤ –≤ –º–µ—Å—è—Ü\", - –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏—Ç –ª—å–≤–æ–≤—è–Ω–∏–Ω.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ú–∏–Ω–∏–º—É–º –º–æ–∂–Ω–æ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—Ç—å 4 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á–∏ –∑–ª–æ—Ç—ã—Ö –≤ –º–µ—Å—è—Ü (–æ–∫–æ–ª–æ 25 —Ç—ã—Å –≥—Ä–Ω), –∞ –º–æ–∂–Ω–æ –∏ 8 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á –∑–ª–æ—Ç—ã—Ö —á–∏—Å—Ç—ã–º–∏ (50 —Ç—ã—Å—è—á –≥—Ä–∏–≤–µ–Ω) - —ç—Ç–æ –µ—Å–ª–∏ –≤—ã–±–∏—Ä–∞—Ç—å —É–¥–∞—á–Ω—ã–µ —Ä–∞–π–æ–Ω—ã –¥–ª—è –ø–æ–µ–∑–¥–æ–∫ –∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å –ø–æ –Ω–æ—á–∞–º. –î–∞–∂–µ –≤ —Å–∞–º—ã–π –Ω–µ—É–¥–∞—á–Ω—ã–π –¥–µ–Ω—å –Ω–∞ \"–£–±–µ—Ä\" –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–∞—Ç—ã–≤–∞—é—Ç –æ–∫–æ–ª–æ 80 –∑–ª–æ—Ç—ã—Ö (500 –≥—Ä–Ω).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ü–æ –µ–≥–æ —Å–ª–æ–≤–∞–º, –∑–∞ –ø–æ–ª–≥–æ–¥–∞ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç—ã –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ –Ω–∞ Uber –æ–Ω –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞–ª –Ω–∞ –ª–∏—á–Ω—ã–π –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–æ–±–∏–ª—å.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–í–∞–∂–Ω–∞ –º–∞—à–∏–Ω–∞. –≠—Ç–æ, –∫–æ–Ω–µ—á–Ω–æ, –Ω–∏ –≤ –∫–æ–µ–º —Å–ª—É—á–∞–µ –Ω–µ \"–ñ–∏–≥—É–ª–∏\". –î–æ–ª–∂–µ–Ω –±—ã—Ç—å –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–æ–±–∏–ª—å –Ω–µ —Å—Ç–∞—Ä—à–µ 2008 –≥–æ–¥–∞, —Å –∫–æ–Ω–¥–∏—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–µ—Ä–æ–º. –Ø, –Ω–∞–ø—Ä–∏–º–µ—Ä, –∞—Ä–µ–Ω–¥—É—é –ú–∏—Ü—É–±–∏—Å–∏ –õ–∞–Ω—Å–µ—Ä. –ü–æ–ø—É–ª—è—Ä–Ω—ã –µ—â–µ –ö–∏–∞, –ü–µ–∂–æ\", - –¥–µ–ª–∏—Ç—Å—è –ó–∞–¥–æ—Ä–æ–∂–Ω—ã–π.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ú–æ–∂–Ω–æ —Ç–∞–∫–∂–µ —Å–æ—Ç—Ä—É–¥–Ω–∏—á–∞—Ç—å —Å –ø–∞—Ä—Ç–Ω–µ—Ä–∞–º–∏ Uber, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ –¥–∞—é—Ç –º–∞—à–∏–Ω—É, —É—Å—Ç–∞–Ω–∞–≤–ª–∏–≤–∞—é—Ç –≥—Ä–∞—Ñ–∏–∫ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç—ã –∏ –±–µ—Ä—É—Ç –æ–∫–æ–ª–æ 15% –¥–æ—Ö–æ–¥–æ–≤.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>–ê—Ç–∞–∫–∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç–æ–≤ –∏ –ø–∞—Å—Å–∞–∂–∏—Ä–æ–≤</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í–ø—Ä–æ—á–µ–º, —Ç–∞–∫—Å–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å –Ω–∞ \"–£–±–µ—Ä–µ\" –≤—Å–µ —Ä–∏—Å–∫–æ–≤–∞–Ω–Ω–µ–µ. –í–æ-–ø–µ—Ä–≤—ã—Ö, –∫–∞–∫ –∏ –≤ –¥—Ä—É–≥–∏—Ö —Å—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–∞—Ö, —ç—Ç–∞ —Å–ª—É–∂–±–∞ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ –¥–µ–π—Å—Ç–≤—É–µ—Ç –ø–æ–ª—É–ª–µ–≥–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ, –∏ –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏–µ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç—ã —É–∂–µ –Ω–µ —Ä–∞–∑ –±–∞—Å—Ç–æ–≤–∞–ª–∏, —Ç—Ä–µ–±—É—è, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–∏&nbsp;UBER –±—Ä–∞–ª–∏ –ª–∏—Ü–µ–Ω–∑–∏–∏, –≤—ã–¥–∞–≤–∞–ª–∏ —á–µ–∫–∏ –∏ –ø–ª–∞—Ç–∏–ª–∏ –Ω–∞–ª–æ–≥–∏, –∫–∞–∫ –∏ –æ–Ω–∏.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ —Ç—Ä–µ–±—É—é—Ç –±–ª–æ–∫–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∫–∏ –º–æ–±–∏–ª—å–Ω—ã—Ö –ø—Ä–∏–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏–π –¥–ª—è –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑–∞ –ø–æ–µ–∑–¥–æ–∫: –≤ –∞–ø—Ä–µ–ª–µ —ç—Ç–æ–≥–æ –≥–æ–¥–∞ –æ–Ω–∏ –ø–µ—Ä–µ–∫—Ä—ã–ª–∏ —É–ª–∏—Ü—ã –∏ –Ω–∞—á–∞–ª–∏ –∑–∞–±–∞—Å—Ç–æ–≤–∫—É.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–ú—ã —Ç—Ä–µ–±—É–µ–º –æ—Ç –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å—Å—Ç–≤–∞, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã –æ–Ω–æ –∑–∞–±–ª–æ–∫–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–ª–æ —ç—Ç–æ –ø—Ä–æ–∫–ª—è—Ç–æ–µ –ø—Ä–∏–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏–µ, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã —É –Ω–∞—Å, –Ω–∞–∫–æ–Ω–µ—Ü, –Ω–∞—Å—Ç–∞–ª –ø–æ–∫–æ–π –∏ –º—ã –º–æ–≥–ª–∏ –Ω–æ—Ä–º–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—Ç—å, –∞ –Ω–µ –ø–æ 15 —á–∞—Å–æ–≤ –≤ —Å—É—Ç–∫–∏\", - –∂–∞–ª–æ–≤–∞–ª—Å—è –≥–ª–∞–≤–∞ –ú–∞–∑–æ–≤–µ—Ü–∫–æ–≥–æ –Ω–µ–∑–∞–≤–∏—Å–∏–º–æ–≥–æ –ø—Ä–æ—Ñ—Å–æ—é–∑–∞ \"–°–æ–ª–∏–¥–∞—Ä–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—å\" –†–∞—Ñ–∞–ª –ü–µ—Ç—Ä –Æ—Ä–µ–∫.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í–ø—Ä–æ—á–µ–º, —ç–∫—Å–ø–µ—Ä—Ç—ã –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä—è—Ç, —á—Ç–æ —Ç–∞–∫–æ–µ –º–∞–ª–æ–≤–µ—Ä–æ—è—Ç–Ω–æ, –ø–æ—Å–∫–æ–ª—å–∫—É —É –ú–∏–Ω–∏—Å—Ç–µ—Ä—Å—Ç–≤–∞ –∏–Ω—Ñ—Ä–∞—Å—Ç—Ä—É–∫—Ç—É—Ä—ã –Ω–µ—Ç –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞ –±–ª–æ–∫–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å –º–æ–±–∏–ª—å–Ω—ã–µ –ø—Ä–∏–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏—è.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ë–ª–æ–∫–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∫–æ–π –¥–æ–ª–∂–Ω—ã –±—ã–ª–∏ –±—ã –∑–∞–Ω—è—Ç—å—Å—è —Ç–µ–ª–µ–∫–æ–º–º—É–Ω–∏–∫–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–Ω—ã–µ –ø—Ä–µ–¥–ø—Ä–∏—è—Ç–∏—è. –ù–æ, –ø–æ –Ω–µ–æ—Ñ–∏—Ü–∏–∞–ª—å–Ω—ã–º –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–º Gazeta Wyborcza, –∫ –æ–ø–µ—Ä–∞—Ç–æ—Ä–∞–º —Å–≤—è–∑–∏ —Ç–∞–∫–∏—Ö –∑–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å–æ–≤ –ø–æ–∫–∞ –Ω–µ –ø–æ—Å—Ç—É–ø–∞–ª–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–•–æ–¥—è—Ç —Å–ª—É—Ö–∏, —á—Ç–æ –æ–±—è–∂—É—Ç –ø–æ–∫—É–ø–∞—Ç—å –ª–∏—Ü–µ–Ω–∑–∏–∏, –∞ –Ω–µ–ª–µ–≥–∞–ª–æ–≤ –±—É–¥—É—Ç —à—Ç—Ä–∞—Ñ–æ–≤–∞—Ç—å. –í –∞—ç—Ä–æ–ø–æ—Ä—Ç—É –í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤—ã —É–∂–µ –Ω–µ —Ä–∞–∑ –±—ã–ª–∏ –∫–æ–Ω—Ñ–ª–∏–∫—Ç—ã –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–µ–π –£–±–µ—Ä–∞ —Å –ø–æ–ª–∏—Ü–∏–µ–π\", - –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏—Ç –ó–∞–¥–æ—Ä–æ–∂–Ω—ã–π.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–π —Ä–∏—Å–∫ - –ø—Ä–∏—Ç–µ—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–∏—è —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏—Ö –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–µ–π. –°–ª—É—á–∞–π –∞—Ç–∞–∫–∏ –Ω–∞ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤, –æ –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–π —Ä–∞—Å—Å–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª –Ω–∞—à —Å–æ–±–µ—Å–µ–¥–Ω–∏–∫, –¥–∞–ª–µ–∫–æ –Ω–µ –µ–¥–∏–Ω–∏—á–µ–Ω. –ì–æ–¥ –Ω–∞–∑–∞–¥ –≤ –≥–æ—Ä–æ–¥–µ –û–ø–æ–ª–µ&nbsp;–ø–æ–ª–∏—Ü–∏—è –∑–∞–¥–µ—Ä–∂–∞–ª–∞ —Ç—Ä–µ—Ö –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–æ–≤, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ —É–Ω–∏–∂–∞–ª–∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç–∞-—É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–∞, –∞ –∑–∞—Ç–µ–º –ø–æ—Ö–∏—Ç–∏–ª–∏ –µ–≥–æ –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–æ–±–∏–ª—å.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–¢—Ä–æ–µ –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–æ–≤ –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª–∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ –ø–æ—Å–ª–µ –ø–æ–ª—É–Ω–æ—á–∏. –ö–æ–≥–¥–∞ –æ–Ω–∏ –ø–æ–Ω—è–ª–∏, —á—Ç–æ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å - –∏–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–µ—Ü, —Ç–æ –Ω–∞—á–∞–ª–∏ –µ–≥–æ —É–Ω–∏–∂–∞—Ç—å. –¢–æ–≥–¥–∞ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç –æ—Å—Ç–∞–Ω–æ–≤–∏–ª –∞–≤—Ç–æ –∏ –≤—ã—à–µ–ª –∏–∑ –Ω–µ–≥–æ, –≤—ã–∑–≤–∞–ª –ø–æ–ª–∏—Ü–∏—é. –ü–æ–∫–∞ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—å —Å–æ–æ–±—â–∞–ª –ø—Ä–∞–≤–æ–æ—Ö—Ä–∞–Ω–∏—Ç–µ–ª—è–º –ø–æ–¥—Ä–æ–±–Ω–æ—Å—Ç–∏ —Å–∏—Ç—É–∞—Ü–∏–∏ –∏ —Å–≤–æ–µ –º–µ—Å—Ç–æ–Ω–∞—Ö–æ–∂–¥–µ–Ω–∏–µ, –æ–¥–∏–Ω –∏–∑ –ø–∞—Å—Å–∞–∂–∏—Ä–æ–≤ —Å–µ–ª –∑–∞ —Ä—É–ª—å –∏ –ø–æ—Ö–∏—Ç–∏–ª –µ–≥–æ. –¢–∞–∫ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ—Ü –æ—Å—Ç–∞–ª—Å—è –±–µ–∑ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏ –Ω–∞ –æ–±–æ—á–∏–Ω–µ. –í–ø–æ—Å–ª–µ–¥—Å—Ç–≤–∏–∏ –ø–æ–ª–∏—Ü–µ–π—Å–∫–∏–µ –∑–∞–¥–µ—Ä–∂–∞–ª–∏ –¥–≤—É—Ö –º—É–∂—á–∏–Ω 22 –∏ 27 –ª–µ—Ç –≤ –≥–æ—Ä–æ–¥–µ –û–ø–æ–ª–µ, –∏–º –ø—Ä–µ–¥—ä—è–≤–∏–ª–∏ –æ–±–≤–∏–Ω–µ–Ω–∏—è –≤ –¥–∏—Å–∫—Ä–∏–º–∏–Ω–∞—Ü–∏–∏ –Ω–∞ –Ω–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ–π –ø–æ—á–≤–µ. –¢—Ä–µ—Ç—å–µ–≥–æ, 32-–ª–µ—Ç–Ω–µ–≥–æ –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–∞, –∑–∞–¥–µ—Ä–∂–∞–ª–∏ –≤ –ö—Ä–∞–∫–æ–≤–µ, –≥–¥–µ —Ç–∞–∫–∂–µ –Ω–∞—à–ª–∏ —É–≥–Ω–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–π –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–æ–±–∏–ª—å\", - —Å–æ–æ–±—â–∞–µ—Ç \"–ü–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–æ–µ —Ä–∞–¥–∏–æ\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–î—Ä—É–≥–æ–π –≥—Ä–æ–º–∫–∏–π –∏–Ω—Ü–∏–¥–µ–Ω—Ç –ø—Ä–æ–∏–∑–æ—à–µ–ª –≤ –º–∞—Ä—Ç–µ —ç—Ç–æ–≥–æ –≥–æ–¥–∞ –≤&nbsp;–í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤–µ - –ø–∞—Å—Å–∞–∂–∏—Ä—ã –Ω–µ —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –æ—Å–∫–æ—Ä–±–ª—è–ª–∏ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–∞-–≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—è Uber, –Ω–æ –∏ –∂–µ—Å—Ç–æ–∫–æ –∏–∑–±–∏–ª–∏.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–û–Ω–∏ —Ç—Ä–µ–±–æ–≤–∞–ª–∏, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã –æ–Ω \"–≤–æ–∑–≤—Ä–∞—â–∞–ª—Å—è –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—É\". –°–Ω–∞—á–∞–ª–∞ –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª—è –Ω–µ—Å–∫–æ–ª—å–∫–æ —Ä–∞–∑ —É–¥–∞—Ä–∏–ª–∏ –≤ —Å–∞–ª–æ–Ω–µ –∞–≤—Ç–æ, –ø–æ—Å–ª–µ —á–µ–≥–æ –≤—ã—Ç–∞—â–∏–ª–∏ –Ω–∞ —É–ª–∏—Ü—É, –≥–¥–µ –ø–æ–≤–∞–ª–∏–ª–∏ –Ω–∞ –∑–µ–º–ª—é –∏ —Å–Ω–æ–≤–∞ –±–∏–ª–∏. –ü–æ—Å–ª–µ —á–µ–≥–æ –ø–æ–≤—Ä–µ–¥–∏–ª–∏ –¥–≤–µ—Ä–∏ –∞–≤—Ç–æ\", - —Å–æ–æ–±—â–∏–ª –∂—É—Ä–Ω–∞–ª–∏—Å—Ç –ü–æ—Ä—Ç–∞–ª–∞ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–∏ PROstir.pl –ï–≤–≥–µ–Ω–∏–π –ü—Ä–∏—Ö–æ–¥—å–∫–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–ï—Å—Ç—å —Å–ª—É—á–∞–∏, –∫–æ–≥–¥–∞ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏—Ö –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–µ–π –∏–∑ \"–£–±–µ—Ä–∞\" –∞—Ç–∞–∫—É—é—Ç –Ω–µ —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –ø–∞—Å—Å–∞–∂–∏—Ä—ã, –Ω–æ –∏ –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏–µ –∫–æ–ª–ª–µ–≥–∏.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–í–∞—Ä—à–∞–≤—Å–∫–∏–µ —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏—Å—Ç—ã –æ–±–∫–ª–µ–∏–≤–∞–ª–∏ –∞–≤—Ç–æ Uber, –≤ –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã—Ö —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—é—Ç —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã, —Ç—Ä—É–¥–Ω–æ —Å–º—ã–≤–∞—é—â–∏–º–∏—Å—è –Ω–∞–∫–ª–µ–π–∫–∞–º–∏ \"–ì–æ–≤–æ—Ä—é —Ç–æ–ª—å–∫–æ –ø–æ-—É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–∏\" –∏ \"–≤–æ—Ä\", - –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏—Ç –Ω–∞–º –ü—Ä–∏—Ö–æ–¥—å–∫–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"width\":590,\"height\":787} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://strana.ua/img/forall/u/10/85/colwidth-c555c207b4eb6a06c6e636eba7a5442f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"787\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>–¢–∞–∫–∏–µ \"–ø–æ–∑–æ—Ä–Ω—ã–µ –Ω–∞–∫–ª–µ–π–∫–∏\" –∫–ª–µ—è—Ç –Ω–∞ –º–∞—à–∏–Ω—ã —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤, —Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—é—â–∏—Ö –Ω–∞ Uber&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í –¶–µ–Ω—Ç—Ä–µ –º–æ–Ω–∏—Ç–æ—Ä–∏–Ω–≥–∞ —Ä–∞—Å–∏—Å—Ç—Å–∫–æ–π –∏ –∫—Å–µ–Ω–æ—Ñ–æ–±—Å–∫–æ–≥–æ –ø–æ–≤–µ–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ –Ω–∞–∑–≤–∞–ª–∏ —Ç–∞–∫–∏–µ –∞–∫—Ü–∏–∏ –ø—É–±–ª–∏—á–Ω—ã–º –æ—Å–∫–æ—Ä–±–ª–µ–Ω–∏–µ–º –ª—é–¥–µ–π –∏–∑-–∑–∞ –∏—Ö –ø—Ä–æ–∏—Å—Ö–æ–∂–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–ú—ã –ø–æ–Ω–∏–º–∞–µ–º —Ç—Ä–µ–±–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏—è –≤–æ–¥–∏—Ç–µ–ª–µ–π —Ç–∞–∫—Å–∏, –º—ã –ø–æ–Ω–∏–º–∞–µ–º –∏—Ö –≥–Ω–µ–≤ –Ω–∞ Uber. –ù–æ —Å—Ä–∞–∂–∞–π—Ç–µ—Å—å —Å –∫–æ–º–ø–∞–Ω–∏–µ–π, —Ç—Ä–µ–±—É–π—Ç–µ –ø—Ä–∞–≤–æ–≤–æ–≥–æ —Ä–µ–≥—É–ª–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∏—è –æ—Ç –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–æ–≥–æ –≥–æ—Å—É–¥–∞—Ä—Å—Ç–≤–∞ –∏ –Ω–µ –Ω–∞–ø–∞–¥–∞–π—Ç–µ –Ω–∞ –ª—é–¥–µ–π, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ, –∫–∞–∫ –∏ –≤—ã, –ø—ã—Ç–∞—é—Ç—Å—è –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–∞—Ç—ã–≤–∞—Ç—å –Ω–∞ –∂–∏–∑–Ω—å, —á—Ç–æ–±—ã —Å–æ–¥–µ—Ä–∂–∞—Ç—å —Å–≤–æ–∏ —Å–µ–º—å–∏\", - –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏—Ç –ü—Ä–∏—Ö–æ–¥—å–∫–æ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>–£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –≤—Å–µ —á–∞—â–µ –æ–±–∏–∂–∞—é—Ç</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–¢–µ–º –≤—Ä–µ–º–µ–Ω–µ–º¬†—É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –≤—Å–µ —á–∞—â–µ —Å—Ç–∞–ª–∫–∏–≤–∞—é—Ç—Å—è —Å –ø—Ä–æ—è–≤–ª–µ–Ω–∏—è–º–∏ –¥–∏—Å–∫—Ä–∏–º–∏–Ω–∞—Ü–∏–∏ –∏ –≤—Ä–∞–∂–¥—ã –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ. –ü—Ä–∏—á–µ–º –∑–∞ –ø–æ—Å–ª–µ–¥–Ω–∏–µ —á–µ—Ç—ã—Ä–µ –≥–æ–¥–∞,¬†–∫–æ–ª–∏—á–µ—Å—Ç–≤–æ —Ç–∞–∫–∏—Ö —Å–ª—É—á–∞–µ–≤ —É–≤–µ–ª–∏—á–∏–ª–æ—Å—å —Å 30 –¥–æ 190, —Å–æ–æ–±—â–∏–ª–∞ —É–ø–æ–ª–Ω–æ–º–æ—á–µ–Ω–Ω–∞—è –í–µ—Ä—Ö–æ–≤–Ω–æ–π –†–∞–¥—ã –ø–æ –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞–º —á–µ–ª–æ–≤–µ–∫–∞ –õ—é–¥–º–∏–ª–∞ –î–µ–Ω–∏—Å–æ–≤–∞.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–ù–µ –≤—Å–µ –≥—Ä–∞–∂–¥–∞–Ω–µ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—ã –æ–±—Ä–∞—â–∞—é—Ç—Å—è –≤ —Å–æ–æ—Ç–≤–µ—Ç—Å—Ç–≤—É—é—â–∏–µ —É—á—Ä–µ–∂–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è, –∫–æ–≥–¥–∞ –Ω–∞—Ä—É—à–∞—é—Ç—Å—è –∏—Ö –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞, –ø–æ—ç—Ç–æ–º—É —ç—Ç–∞ —Ü–∏—Ñ—Ä–∞ –º–æ–∂–µ—Ç –±—ã—Ç—å –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ\", - –Ω–∞–ø–∏—Å–∞–ª–∞ –î–µ–Ω–∏—Å–æ–≤–∞ –Ω–∞ —Å–≤–æ–µ–π —Å—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–∏—Ü–µ –≤ Facebook.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>–í –∫–∞—á–µ—Å—Ç–≤–µ –ø—Ä–∏–º–µ—Ä–∞ –æ–Ω–∞ –ø—Ä–∏–≤–µ–ª–∞ –∂–µ—Å—Ç–æ–∫–æ–µ –∏–∑–±–∏–µ–Ω–∏–µ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Å–∫–æ–≥–æ —Å—Ç—É–¥–µ–Ω—Ç–∞ –≥—Ä—É–ø–ø–æ–π –∏–∑ –ø—è—Ç–∏ —á–µ–ª–æ–≤–µ–∫ –≤ –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–æ–º –≥–æ—Ä–æ–¥–µ –ñ–æ—Ä—ã 20 —Å–µ–Ω—Ç—è–±—Ä—è.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"–ü–æ—Å–ª–µ –ú–∞–π–¥–∞–Ω–∞ –∏ –Ω–∞—á–∞–ª–∞ –≤–æ–π–Ω—ã –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ –∏ –ø–∞–¥–µ–Ω–∏—è —É—Ä–æ–≤–Ω—è –∂–∏–∑–Ω–∏ –Ω–∞–ø–ª—ã–≤ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü–µ–≤ –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à—É –≤—ã—Ä–æ—Å. –° –æ–¥–Ω–æ–π —Å—Ç–æ—Ä–æ–Ω—ã, —ç—Ç–æ —Ö–æ—Ä–æ—à–æ, –Ω–∞–º –Ω–µ —Ö–≤–∞—Ç–∞–µ—Ç —Ä–∞–±–æ—á–∏—Ö —Ä—É–∫, –Ω–æ —á–∞—Å—Ç—å –ø–æ–ª—è–∫–æ–≤ —Å—á–∏—Ç–∞–µ—Ç, —á—Ç–æ –∏–∑-–∑–∞ —Ç–æ–≥–æ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã —Å–æ–≥–ª–∞—Å–Ω—ã –Ω–∞ –º–µ–Ω—å—à—É—é –∑–∞—Ä–ø–ª–∞—Ç—É, —É –Ω–∏—Ö –ø–∞–¥–∞—é—Ç –∑–∞—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∫–∏. –¢–∞–∫–∂–µ –∞–∫—Ç–∏–≤–∏–∑–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–ª–∏—Å—å –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏–µ –Ω–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–∞–ª–∏—Å—Ç—ã, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–º –Ω–µ –Ω—Ä–∞–≤–∏—Ç—Å—è –ø—Ä–æ—Å–ª–∞–≤–ª–µ–Ω–∏–µ –ë–∞–Ω–¥–µ—Ä—ã –≤ –£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω–µ, –∏ –∞–≤—Ç–æ–º–∞—Ç–∏—á–µ—Å–∫–∏ –≤—Å–µ —É–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã, –∫–æ—Ç–æ—Ä—ã–µ –ø—Ä–∏–µ–∑–∂–∞—é—Ç –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à—É, —ç—Ç–æ \"–±–∞–Ω–¥–µ—Ä–æ–≤—Ü—ã\", - –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏—Ç \"–°—Ç—Ä–∞–Ω–µ\" –ø–æ–ª—å—Å–∫–∏–π –∂—É—Ä–Ω–∞–ª–∏—Å—Ç –ú–∞—Ä—á–∏–Ω –ö–æ–≤–∞–ª—å—á–∏–∫.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '–£–∫—Ä–∞–∏–Ω—Ü—ã –∞—Ä–µ–Ω–¥—É—é—Ç –º–∞—à–∏–Ω—ã –≤ –ü–æ–ª—å—à–µ –∏ —Ç–∞–∫—Å—É—é—Ç –ø–æ —Ç—Ä–∏ –º–µ—Å—è—Ü–∞', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '399-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '', 399, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/02/25/399-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(402, 1, '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrainians are mastering a new kind of earnings in Poland. If earlier mass went to the construction sites, now are arranged taxi drivers Uber and Bolt, who work through mobile applications.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Profit - from 25 to 50 thousand hryvnias.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To do this, you need only a driver&#39;s license - you can tax on &quot;visa-free&quot; three months without permits, then return to Ukraine for three months and again go to work.¬† ¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since their cars with Ukrainian license plates drivers can not work, rent cars in Poland - an average of 500 zlotys per week (3 thousand hryvnia).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But there are also pitfalls - Ukrainian drivers are increasingly complaining of harassment because of their nationality.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Country&quot; learned how Ukrainians work as taxi drivers in Poland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>For six months i earned on my car¬†</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;In Poland, it is much more likely to meet a Ukrainian driver in a taxi than a Pole. In some locals it is irritating. My friend, who also works in Warsaw, was attacked by two young clients when they realized that he was Ukrainian. Like, what you came here, &quot;banderovets&quot;, shouted to &quot;roll back to Ukraine&quot; - told us Lvivian Vladimir zarozhnyy, who is taxiing in Warsaw.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The easiest way to get a job is Uber, which has been working in the largest and most popular Polish cities for the last five years: Warsaw, Krakow, Gdansk. It is more popular than simple taxis and earnings there are higher.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to him, it is most profitable to work in Warsaw - there are a lot of orders.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;I pay tax - in translation on our money 7 thousand hryvnias per car, about 5% of the profits I give to the company. It is good that the owner himself, there are no bosses, I build a schedule for myself. And most importantly - I earn about twice as much as in Ukraine. There are more orders, people have more money (although the tariff is about the same - about 50 hryvnia simulopers for 3 kilometers). Only rights, a certificate of criminal record and a machine are needed for work. In Poland, I shoot a corner for 200 dollars a month,&quot; says Lvivian.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Minimum you can earn 4 thousand zlotys per month (about 25 thousand UAH), and you can 8 thousand zloty slotnet pure (50 thousand hryvnia) - this is if you choose the successful areas for travel and tact at night. Even on the worst day, Uber in Poland earns about 80 zlotys (500 UAH).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to him, during six months of work in Poland on Uber, he earned a personal car.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;The car is important. This, of course, is by no means &quot;Jiguli.&quot; Must be a car no older than 2008, with air conditioning. I, for one, rent a Mitsubishi Lancer. There is also a popular Kea, Peugeot,&quot; says The Road.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can also work with Uber partners who give a car, set a schedule and take about 15% of the revenue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Attacks of taxi drivers and passengers</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, taxing on &quot;Uber&quot; is all the riskier. First, as in other countries, this taxi service operates semi-legally, and Polish taxi drivers have repeatedly gone on strike, demanding that UBER drivers take licenses, issue checks and pay taxes, as they do.¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Warsaw, taxi drivers demand the blocking of mobile applications for booking trips: in April this year, they blocked the streets and began a strike.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;We demand that the government block this damn application, so that we finally have peace and we can work normally, not 15 hours a day,&quot; complained the head of the Mazowiecki independent trade union &quot;Solidarity&quot; Rafal Piotr Jurek.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, experts say this is unlikely, as the Ministry of Infrastructure does not have the right to block mobile applications.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Telecommunications companies would have to deal with the blocking. But, according to unofficial data of Gazeta Wyborcza, the telecom operators have not yet received such requests.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;There are rumors that they will be obliged to buy licenses, and illegals will be fined. There have been more and more conflicts between Uber drivers and the police at Warsaw airport,&quot; he said.¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The second risk is harassment of Ukrainian drivers. The case of the attack on ukrainians, about which our interlocutor told, is far from unique. A year ago in the city of Opol police detained three Poles who humiliated a Ukrainian taxi driver, and then stole his car.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Three Poles ordered a taxi after midnight. When they realized that the driver - a foreigner, they began to humiliate him. Then the taxi driver stopped the car and got out of it, called the police. While the driver told law enforcement details of the situation and his whereabouts, one of the passengers got behind the wheel and kidnapped him. So the Ukrainian was left without a taxi on the side of the road. Police subsequently detained two men, aged 22 and 27, in the city of Opol and charged with discrimination on national grounds. The third, a 32-year-old Pole, was detained in Krakow, where a stolen car was also found,&quot; Polish Radio reports.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Another high-profile incident occurred in March this year in Warsaw - passengers not only insulted the Ukrainian driver of Uber, but also severely beaten.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;They demanded that he &quot;return to Ukraine.&quot; At first, the driver was hit several times in the car, then dragged into the street, where they were knocked to the ground and beaten again. After that, the doors of the car were damaged,&quot; said Yevgeny Prikhodko, a journalist at the Portal of Ukrainians of Poland PROstir.pl.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are cases when Ukrainian drivers from &quot;Uber&quot; are attacked not only by passengers, but also by Polish colleagues.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Warsaw taxi drivers pasted Uber cars, in which Ukrainians work, hard to wash off stickers &quot;I speak only Ukrainian&quot; and &quot;thief&quot; - says to us Prikhodko.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"width\":590,\"height\":787} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://strana.ua/img/forall/u/10/85/colwidth-c555c207b4eb6a06c6e636eba7a5442f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"787\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Such &quot;shameful stickers&quot; are glued to the cars of Ukrainians working for Uber¬†¬†</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Centre for the Monitoring of Racist and Xenophobic Behaviour in Poland called such actions a public insult to people because of their origin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;We understand the demands of taxi drivers, we understand their anger at Uber. But fight the company, demand legal regulation from the Polish state and do not attack people who, like you, are trying to make a living to support their families,&quot; Prikhodko said.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Ukrainians are increasingly offended</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Meanwhile, Ukrainians are increasingly faced with discrimination and hostility in Poland. And over the past four years, the number of such cases has increased from 30 to 190, said Lyudmila Denisova, parliamentary commissioner for human rights.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Not all citizens of Ukraine apply to the relevant institutions when their rights are violated, so this figure may be higher,&quot; Denisova wrote on her Facebook page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As an example, she cited the brutal beating of a Ukrainian student by a group of five in the Polish city of Jora on September 20.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;After the Maidan and the beginning of the war in Ukraine and the fall in living standards, the influx of Ukrainians to Poland grew. On the one hand, it is good, we do not have enough workers, but some Poles believe that because Ukrainians agree to lower wages, their earnings fall. Polish nationalists who do not like the glorification of Bandera in Ukraine have also stepped up, and automatically all Ukrainians who come to Poland are &quot;banderites,&quot; Polish journalist Marcin Kowalczyk tells &quot;Country&quot;.¬† ¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ukrainians rent cars in Poland and taxi for three months', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%d1%83%d0%ba%d1%80%d0%b0%d0%b0%b0%bd%d1%86%d1%8b-%d0%b0%d1%80%d0%b5%d0%d0%bd%d0%b4%d1%83-%d1%8e%d1%82-%d0%d0%d0%b0%d1%88%d0%b8%d0%bd%d1%8b-%d0%b2-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%bb%d1%8c%d1-88%d0%b5-%d0%b8-%d1%82%d0', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=399', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(403, 1, '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrai≈Ñcy opanowali nowy rodzaj zarobk√≥w w Polsce. Je≈õli wcze≈õniej masa uda≈Ç siƒô do budowy, teraz sƒÖ u≈Ço≈ºone taks√≥wkarzy Uber i Bolt, kt√≥rzy pracujƒÖ za po≈õrednictwem aplikacji mobilnych.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zysk - od 25 do 50 tysiƒôcy hrywien.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Aby to zrobiƒá, potrzebujesz tylko prawa jazdy - mo≈ºesz opodatkowaƒá &quot;bezwizowy&quot; trzy miesiƒÖce bez zezwole≈Ñ, a nastƒôpnie wr√≥ciƒá na Ukrainƒô na trzy miesiƒÖce i ponownie i≈õƒá do pracy.¬† ¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Poniewa≈º ich samochody z ukrai≈Ñskimi tablicami rejestracyjnymi kierowcy nie mogƒÖ pracowaƒá, wynajmƒÖ samochody w Polsce - ≈õrednio 500 z≈Çotych tygodniowo (3 tysiƒÖce hrywien).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ale sƒÖ te≈º pu≈Çapki - ukrai≈Ñscy kierowcy coraz czƒô≈õciej skar≈ºƒÖ siƒô na molestowanie ze wzglƒôdu na ich narodowo≈õƒá.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Kraj&quot; dowiedzia≈Ç siƒô, jak Ukrai≈Ñcy pracujƒÖ jako taks√≥wkarze w Polsce.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Przez sze≈õƒá miesiƒôcy zarabia≈Çem na moim samochodzie¬†</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;W Polsce znacznie czƒô≈õciej spotyka siƒô ukrai≈Ñskiego kierowcƒô w taks√≥wce ni≈º Polak. U niekt√≥rych mieszka≈Ñc√≥w jest to irytujƒÖce. M√≥j przyjaciel, kt√≥ry r√≥wnie≈º pracuje w Warszawie, zosta≈Ç zaatakowany przez dw√≥ch m≈Çodych klient√≥w, gdy zdali sobie sprawƒô, ≈ºe jest Ukrai≈Ñcem. Jak, co tu przyszed≈Çe≈õ, &quot;banderovets&quot;, krzycza≈Ç do &quot;powrotu na Ukrainƒô&quot; - powiedzia≈Ç nam Lvivian Vladimir zarozhnyy, kt√≥ry ko≈Çuje w Warszawie.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Najprostszym sposobem na zdobycie pracy jest Uber, kt√≥ry od piƒôciu lat pracuje w najwiƒôkszych i najpopularniejszych polskich miastach: Warszawie, Krakowie, Gda≈Ñsku. Jest bardziej popularny ni≈º proste taks√≥wki i zarobki sƒÖ wy≈ºsze.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wed≈Çug niego najbardziej op≈Çaca siƒô pracowaƒá w Warszawie - jest du≈ºo zam√≥wie≈Ñ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;P≈Çacƒô podatek - w t≈Çumaczeniu na nasze pieniƒÖdze 7 tysiƒôcy hrywien na samoch√≥d, oko≈Ço 5% zysk√≥w dajƒô firmie. Dobrze, ≈ºe sam w≈Ça≈õciciel, nie ma szef√≥w, budujƒô harmonogram dla siebie. A co najwa≈ºniejsze - zarabiam oko≈Ço dwa razy wiƒôcej ni≈º na Ukrainie. Jest wiƒôcej zam√≥wie≈Ñ, ludzie majƒÖ wiƒôcej pieniƒôdzy (chocia≈º taryfa jest prawie taka sama - oko≈Ço 50 hrywien simulopers na 3 kilometry). Do pracy potrzebne sƒÖ tylko prawa, za≈õwiadczenie o karalno≈õci i maszyna. W Polsce strzelam za 200 dolar√≥w miesiƒôcznie ‚Äì m√≥wi Lvivian.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Minimum mo≈ºna zarobiƒá 4 tysiƒÖce z≈Çotych miesiƒôcznie (oko≈Ço 25 tysiƒôcy UAH), a mo≈ºesz 8 tysiƒôcy z≈Çotych slotnet czysty (50 tysiƒôcy hrywien) - to jest, je≈õli wybierzesz udane obszary podr√≥≈ºy i taktu w nocy. Nawet w najgorszym dniu Uber w Polsce zarabia oko≈Ço 80 z≈Çotych (500 UAH).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Wed≈Çug niego, podczas sze≈õciu miesiƒôcy pracy w Polsce nad Uberem, zarobi≈Ç samoch√≥d osobowy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Samoch√≥d jest wa≈ºny. To, oczywi≈õcie, nie jest w ≈ºaden spos√≥b &quot;Jiguli&quot;. Musi byƒá samoch√≥d nie starszy ni≈º 2008, z klimatyzacjƒÖ. Ja, na przyk≈Çad, wynajƒÖƒá Mitsubishi Lancer. Istnieje r√≥wnie≈º popularny Kea, Peugeot&quot;, m√≥wi The Road.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mo≈ºesz r√≥wnie≈º wsp√≥≈Çpracowaƒá z partnerami Uber, kt√≥rzy podajƒÖ samoch√≥d, ustalajƒÖ harmonogram i zajmujƒÖ oko≈Ço 15% przychod√≥w.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Ataki taks√≥wkarzy i pasa≈ºer√≥w</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jednak opodatkowanie &quot;Ubera&quot; jest bardziej ryzykowne. Po pierwsze, podobnie jak w innych krajach, ta taks√≥wka dzia≈Ça p√≥≈Çlegalnie, a polscy taks√≥wkarze wielokrotnie strajkowali, domagajƒÖc siƒô, aby kierowcy UBER przyjmowali licencje, wystawiali czeki i p≈Çacili podatki, tak jak oni.¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>W Warszawie taks√≥wkarze domagajƒÖ siƒô zablokowania aplikacji mobilnych na rezerwacjƒô wycieczek: w kwietniu tego roku zablokowali ulice i rozpoczƒôli strajk.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Domagamy siƒô, aby rzƒÖd zablokowa≈Ç ten cholerny wniosek, aby≈õmy w reszcie mieli spok√≥j i mogli≈õmy pracowaƒá normalnie, a nie 15 godzin dziennie&quot; ‚Äì skar≈ºy≈Ç siƒô szef mazowieckiego niezale≈ºnego zwiƒÖzku zawodowego &quot;Solidarno≈õƒá&quot; Rafa≈Ç Piotr Jurek.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Eksperci twierdzƒÖ jednak, ≈ºe jest to ma≈Ço prawdopodobne, poniewa≈º Ministerstwo Infrastruktury nie ma prawa blokowaƒá aplikacji mobilnych.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Firmy telekomunikacyjne musia≈Çyby radziƒá sobie z blokowaniem. Ale wed≈Çug nieoficjalnych danych &quot;Gazety Wyborczej&quot;, operatorzy telekomunikacyjni nie otrzymali jeszcze takich wniosk√≥w.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;KrƒÖ≈ºƒÖ pog≈Çoski, ≈ºe bƒôdƒÖ zobowiƒÖzani do zakupu licencji, a nielegalni zostanƒÖ ukarani grzywnƒÖ. Na lotnisku w Warszawie dochodzi do coraz wiƒôkszej liczby konflikt√≥w miƒôdzy kierowcami Ubera a policjƒÖ&quot; - powiedzia≈Ç.¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drugim zagro≈ºeniem jest nƒôkanie ukrai≈Ñskich kierowc√≥w. Sprawa ataku na Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w, o kt√≥rym m√≥wi≈Ç nasz rozm√≥wca, nie jest wyjƒÖtkowa. Rok temu w mie≈õcie Opol policja zatrzyma≈Ça trzech Polak√≥w, kt√≥rzy upokorzyli ukrai≈Ñskiego taks√≥wkarza, a nastƒôpnie ukradli jego samoch√≥d.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Trzech Polak√≥w zam√≥wi≈Ço taks√≥wkƒô po p√≥≈Çnocy. Kiedy zdali sobie sprawƒô, ≈ºe kierowca - cudzoziemiec, zaczƒôli go poni≈ºaƒá. Nastƒôpnie taks√≥wkarz zatrzyma≈Ç samoch√≥d i wysiad≈Ç z niego, wezwa≈Ç policjƒô. Podczas gdy kierowca opowiedzia≈Ç organom ≈õcigania o szczeg√≥≈Çach sytuacji i jego miejscu pobytu, jeden z pasa≈ºer√≥w wsiad≈Ç za kierownicƒô i porwa≈Ç go. Tak wiƒôc Ukrai≈Ñca pozostawiono bez taks√≥wki na poboczu drogi. Nastƒôpnie policja zatrzyma≈Ça dw√≥ch mƒô≈ºczyzn w wieku 22 i 27 lat w mie≈õcie Opol i oskar≈ºonych o dyskryminacjƒô ze wzglƒôd√≥w krajowych. Trzeci, 32-letni Polak, zosta≈Ç zatrzymany w Krakowie, gdzie znaleziono r√≥wnie≈º skradziony samoch√≥d&quot; - donosi Polskie Radio.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kolejny g≈Ço≈õny incydent mia≈Ç miejsce w marcu tego roku w Warszawie - pasa≈ºerowie nie tylko obra≈ºali ukrai≈Ñskiego kierowcƒô Ubera, ale tak≈ºe dotkliwie bici.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Domagali siƒô, aby &quot;wr√≥ci≈Ç na Ukrainƒô&quot;. PoczƒÖtkowo kierowca zosta≈Ç uderzony kilka razy w samoch√≥d, a nastƒôpnie wciƒÖgniƒôty na ulicƒô, gdzie zosta≈Ç powalony na ziemiƒô i pobity ponownie. Nastƒôpnie drzwi samochodu zosta≈Çy uszkodzone&quot; - powiedzia≈Ç Jewgienij Prichodko, dziennikarz portalu Ukrai≈Ñskiego PROstir.pl.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ZdajƒÖ siƒô przypadki, gdy ukrai≈Ñscy kierowcy z &quot;Ubera&quot; sƒÖ atakowani nie tylko przez pasa≈ºer√≥w, ale tak≈ºe przez polskich koleg√≥w.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Warszawscy taks√≥wkarze wkleili samochody Ubera, w kt√≥rych pracujƒÖ Ukrai≈Ñcy, ciƒô≈ºko zmyƒá naklejki &quot;M√≥wiƒô tylko ukrai≈Ñska&quot; i &quot;z≈Çodziej&quot; - m√≥wi nam Prichodko.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"width\":590,\"height\":787} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://strana.ua/img/forall/u/10/85/colwidth-c555c207b4eb6a06c6e636eba7a5442f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"787\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Takie &quot;haniebne naklejki&quot; sƒÖ przyklejone do samochod√≥w Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w pracujƒÖcych dla Ubera¬†¬†</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>O≈õrodek Monitorowania Zachowa≈Ñ Rasistowskich i Ksenofobicznych w Polsce nazwa≈Ç takie dzia≈Çania publicznƒÖ zniewagƒÖ dla ludzi ze wzglƒôdu na ich pochodzenie.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Rozumiemy wymagania taks√≥wkarzy, rozumiemy ich gniew na Ubera. Ale walcz z firmƒÖ, ≈ºƒÖdaj regulacji prawnych od pa≈Ñstwa polskiego i nie atakuj ludzi, kt√≥rzy tak jak ty starajƒÖ siƒô zarabiaƒá na ≈ºycie, aby utrzymaƒá swoje rodziny&quot;, powiedzia≈Ç Prikhodko.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Ukrai≈Ñcy sƒÖ coraz bardziej obra≈ºeni</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tymczasem Ukrai≈Ñcy coraz czƒô≈õciej borykajƒÖ siƒô z dyskryminacjƒÖ i wrogo≈õciƒÖ w Polsce. W ciƒÖgu ostatnich czterech lat liczba takich przypadk√≥w wzros≈Ça z 30 do 190 , powiedzia≈Ça Ludmi≈Ça Denisowa, parlamentarna komisarz do spraw praw cz≈Çowieka.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Nie wszyscy obywatele Ukrainy majƒÖ zastosowanie do odpowiednich instytucji, gdy ich prawa sƒÖ naruszane, wiƒôc liczba ta mo≈ºe byƒá wy≈ºsza&quot;, napisa≈Ça Denisova na swojej stronie na Facebooku.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Jako przyk≈Çad, ona przytoczy≈Ça brutalne pobicie ukrai≈Ñskiego studenta przez grupƒô piƒôciu w polskim mie≈õcie Jora 20 wrze≈õnia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&quot;Po Majdanie i rozpoczƒôciu wojny na Ukrainie i spadku poziomu ≈ºycia, nap≈Çyw Ukrai≈Ñc√≥w do Polski wzr√≥s≈Ç. Z jednej strony jest dobrze, nie mamy wystarczajƒÖcej liczby pracownik√≥w, ale niekt√≥rzy Polacy uwa≈ºajƒÖ, ≈ºe poniewa≈º Ukrai≈Ñcy zgadzajƒÖ siƒô na ni≈ºsze p≈Çace, ich zarobki spadajƒÖ. Nasilili siƒô tak≈ºe polscy nacjonali≈õci, kt√≥rzy nie lubiƒÖ gloryfikacji Bandery na Ukrainie, a automatycznie wszyscy Ukrai≈Ñcy przyje≈ºd≈ºajƒÖcy do Polski sƒÖ &quot;bandytami&quot;, m√≥wi &quot;Country&quot;.¬† ¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ukrai≈Ñcy wynajmujƒÖ samochody w Polsce i taks√≥wkƒô na trzy miesiƒÖce', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%d1%83%d0%ba%d1%80%d0%b0%d0%b0%b0%bd%d1%86%d1%8b-%d0%b0%d1%80%d0%b5%d0%d0%d0%bd%d0%b4%d1%83-%d1%8e%d1%82-%d0%d0%d0%b0%d1%88%d0%b8%bd%d1%8b-%d0%b2-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%bb%d1%8c%d1-88%d0%b5-%d0%b8-%d1%82%d0', '', '', '2020-02-25 17:59:50', '2020-02-25 14:59:50', '', 0, 'http://blessed-firm.com/?p=399', 0, 'post', '', 0),
