(486, 1, '2020-06-06 15:13:04', '2020-06-06 12:13:04', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":474,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://blessed-firm.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ZDMkmNBiJAUk-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-474\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">Ukrainka zmieni≈Ça nazwisko ze wzglƒôdu na Polskƒô, ale zosta≈Ça ujawniona\nObywatel Ukrainy pr√≥bujƒÖcy nielegalnie przekroczyƒá granicƒô z PolskƒÖ zosta≈Ç zatrzymany w Grebennoye.\n\n\nWed≈Çug Yavp.pl, powo≈ÇujƒÖc siƒô na stronƒô internetowƒÖ Departamentu Stra≈ºy Granicznej w Nadbu≈ºanach, 51-letnia kobieta zmieni≈Ça swoje dane osobowe, gdy zabroniono jej wjazdu do Polski i kraj√≥w strefy Schengen.\n\nPrzyjƒô≈Ça nowe imiƒô i nowy paszport. Nadal jednak nie uda≈Ço jej siƒô oszukaƒá stra≈ºy granicznej. Podczas szczeg√≥≈Çowej kontroli ustalili, ≈ºe obywatel Ukrainy jest osobƒÖ niepo≈ºƒÖdanƒÖ w Polsce.\n\nKobieta zosta≈Ça zatrzymana i wr√≥ci≈Ça na Ukrainƒô po zako≈Ñczeniu wszystkich procedur administracyjnych i proceduralnych.</pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '¬†Zmieni≈Çem swoje imiƒô i nazwisko, ale co≈õ posz≈Ço nie tak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '478-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-06 15:13:04', '2020-06-06 12:13:04', '', 478, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/06/06/478-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(487, 1, '2020-06-06 15:14:46', '2020-06-06 12:14:46', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>¬†<br> ¬†</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":474,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://blessed-firm.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ZDMkmNBiJAUk-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-474\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrainka changed her last name for the sake of Poland, but she was exposed<br>\nA Ukrainian citizen trying to cross the border with Poland illegally was detained in Grebennoye.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to Yavp.pl, citing the website of the Nadbu≈æany Department of the Border Guard Service, a 51-year-old woman changed her personal data while being banned from entering Poland and the Schengen countries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She took a new name and a new passport. However, she still failed to deceive the border guards. During a detailed inspection, they established that the Ukrainian citizen was an undesirable person in Poland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The woman was detained and returned to Ukraine after completing all administrative and procedural procedures.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '¬†–°hanged my name, but something went wrong', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '476-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-06 15:14:46', '2020-06-06 12:14:46', '', 476, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/06/06/476-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(488, 1, '2020-06-06 15:16:44', '2020-06-06 12:16:44', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ukrainka zmieni≈Ça nazwisko ze wzglƒôdu na Polskƒô, ale zosta≈Ça ujawniona<br>Obywatel Ukrainy pr√≥bujƒÖcy nielegalnie przekroczyƒá granicƒô z PolskƒÖ zosta≈Ç zatrzymany w Grebennoye.<br><br><br>Wed≈Çug Yavp.pl, powo≈ÇujƒÖc siƒô na stronƒô internetowƒÖ Departamentu Stra≈ºy Granicznej w Nadbu≈ºanach, 51-letnia kobieta zmieni≈Ça swoje dane osobowe, gdy zabroniono jej wjazdu do Polski i kraj√≥w strefy Schengen.<br><br>Przyjƒô≈Ça nowe imiƒô i nowy paszport. Nadal jednak nie uda≈Ço jej siƒô oszukaƒá stra≈ºy granicznej. Podczas szczeg√≥≈Çowej kontroli ustalili, ≈ºe obywatel Ukrainy jest osobƒÖ niepo≈ºƒÖdanƒÖ w Polsce.<br><br>Kobieta zosta≈Ça zatrzymana i wr√≥ci≈Ça na Ukrainƒô po zako≈Ñczeniu wszystkich procedur administracyjnych i proceduralnych.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '¬†Zmieni≈Çem swoje imiƒô i nazwisko, ale co≈õ posz≈Ço nie tak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '478-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-06 15:16:44', '2020-06-06 12:16:44', '', 478, 'http://blessed-firm.com/2020/06/06/478-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
