(820, 1, '2020-10-16 17:31:43', '2020-10-16 14:31:43', 'And all because of the fact that last Saturday, October 10, the Polish government decided to tighten control over the wearing of masks on the street due to the spread of coronavirus infection.\r\n\r\nFrom Saturday in Poland, people are obliged to cover their mouths and noses not only in public places, but also in the open air. This means that you cannot take off your mask to drink or eat on the street - it is possible that a person will be fined for such actions.\r\n\r\nThe Chief Sanitary Inspectorate notes that there are no regulations that would revoke the order to wear a mask on people who eat food on the street. This means that if you get hungry while walking around the city and decide to eat a sandwich or a hot dog, you may be fined by the police.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-818 alignleft\" src=\"https://blessed-firm.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e90718c6154b194199494-2-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"158\" />On the sanepid website, in the section \"Questions and answers about food and coronavirus\" you can find the following information:</p>\r\n‚ÄúThe requirement to cover your mouth and nose applies to everyone on the streets, in offices, shops, service areas and workplaces. It does not contain exceptions for the consumption of food, ice cream, waffles, hot dogs, etc. in places where the obligation to wear masks applies. \"\r\n\r\nPay attention to the news on this topic:\r\nDon\'t you want to wear a mask in Poland? Get permission from a doctor or pay a fine!\r\nRestaurant week in Wroclaw or where to eat gourmet meals for‚Ä¶\r\nDo you want to cross the Polish-Ukrainian border? Pay 50 zlotys for 500 meters!\r\nDo you want to sit on a plane with your husband or wife? Pay 12 euros!\r\nDo you want to get rid of old furniture? Be careful not to get a fine\r\nPoland wants to allow beavers to eat', 'If you want to eat or drink something on the street in Poland, pay a fine', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '808-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-16 17:31:43', '2020-10-16 14:31:43', '', 808, 'https://blessed-firm.com/blog/2020/10/16/808-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(821, 1, '2020-10-16 17:33:22', '2020-10-16 14:33:22', 'A wszystko za sprawƒÖ tego, ≈ºe w minionƒÖ sobotƒô 10 pa≈∫dziernika polski rzƒÖd podjƒÖ≈Ç decyzjƒô o zaostrzeniu kontroli nad noszeniem masek na ulicy w zwiƒÖzku z rozprzestrzenianiem siƒô zaka≈ºenia koronawirusem.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-823 alignleft\" src=\"https://blessed-firm.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e90718c6154b194199494-3-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"158\" />Od soboty w Polsce ludzie majƒÖ obowiƒÖzek zakrywania ust i nosa nie tylko w miejscach publicznych, ale tak≈ºe na ≈õwie≈ºym powietrzu. Oznacza to, ≈ºe nie mo≈ºesz zdjƒÖƒá maski, aby piƒá lub je≈õƒá na ulicy - mo≈ºliwe, ≈ºe za takie dzia≈Çania dana osoba zostanie ukarana grzywnƒÖ.\r\n\r\nG≈Ç√≥wny Inspektorat Sanitarny zwraca uwagƒô, ≈ºe nie ma przepis√≥w, kt√≥re uniewa≈ºnia≈Çyby nakaz noszenia maski osobom spo≈ºywajƒÖcym jedzenie na ulicy. Oznacza to, ≈ºe je≈õli zg≈Çodniejesz spacerujƒÖc po mie≈õcie i zdecydujesz siƒô zje≈õƒá kanapkƒô lub hot doga, policja mo≈ºe ukaraƒá mandatem.\r\n\r\nNa stronie sanepidu w sekcji ‚ÄûPytania i odpowiedzi dotyczƒÖce ≈ºywno≈õci i koronawirusa‚Äù mo≈ºna znale≈∫ƒá nastƒôpujƒÖce informacje:\r\n\r\n‚ÄûWym√≥g zakrywania ust i nosa dotyczy ka≈ºdego na ulicy, w biurach, sklepach, miejscach us≈Çugowych i miejscach pracy. Nie zawiera wyjƒÖtk√≥w dotyczƒÖcych spo≈ºywania jedzenia, lod√≥w, gofr√≥w, hot dog√≥w itp. W miejscach, w kt√≥rych obowiƒÖzuje obowiƒÖzek noszenia masek. \"', 'Je≈õli chcesz co≈õ zje≈õƒá lub wypiƒá na ulicy w Polsce, zap≈Çaƒá grzywn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jesli-chcesz-cos-zjesc-lub-wypic-na-ulicy-w-polsce-zaplac-grzywn', '', '', '2020-10-16 17:33:22', '2020-10-16 14:33:22', '', 0, 'https://blessed-firm.com/?p=821', 0, 'post', '', 0),
